637 
638 class CreateToolTip(object):
639 
640  def __init__(self, widget, text='widget info'):
641  self.waittime = 500 #miliseconds
642  self.wraplength = 100 #pixels
643  self.widget = widget
644  self.text = text
645  self.widget.bind("<Enter>", self.enter)
646  self.widget.bind("<Leave>", self.leave)
647  self.widget.bind("<ButtonPress>", self.leave)
648  self.id = None
649  self.tw = None
650 
651  def enter(self, event=None):
652  self.schedule()
653 
654  def leave(self, event=None):
655  self.unschedule()
656  self.hidetip()
657 
658  def schedule(self):
659  self.unschedule()
660  self.id = self.widget.after(self.waittime, self.showtip)
661 
662  def unschedule(self):
663  id = self.id
664  self.id = None
665  if id:
666  self.widget.after_cancel(id)
667 
668  def showtip(self, event=None):
669  x = y = 0
670  x, y, cx, cy = self.widget.bbox("insert")
671  x += self.widget.winfo_rootx() + 25
672  y += self.widget.winfo_rooty() + 20
673  # creates a toplevel window
674  self.tw = Toplevel(self.widget)
675  # Leaves only the label and removes the app window
676  self.tw.wm_overrideredirect(True)
677  self.tw.wm_geometry("+%d+%d" % (x, y))
678  label = Label(self.tw, text=self.text, justify='left',
679  background="#ffffe0", relief='solid', borderwidth=1,
680  wraplength = self.wraplength)
681  label.pack(ipadx=1)
682 
683  def hidetip(self):
684  tw = self.tw
685  self.tw= None
686  if tw:
687  tw.destroy()
688 #
689 # =========== Start widgets routines =============================
690

1452 def BSaveData():
1453  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, SAMPLErate
1454 
1455  # open file to save data
1456  filename = asksaveasfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")])
1457  DataFile = open(filename, 'w')
1458  DataFile.write( 'Sample-#, CA-V, CA-I, CB-V, CB-I \n' )
1459  for index in range(len(VBuffA)):
1460  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1461  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffA[index]) + ', ' + str(IBuffA[index]) + ', '
1462  + str(VBuffB[index]) + ', ' + str(IBuffB[index]) + '\n')

1465 def BSaveChannelData():
1466  global SAMPLErate, VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB
1467 
1468  # ask user for channel to save
1469  Channel = askstring("Choose Channel", "CA-V, CB-V, CA-I or CB-I\n\nChannel:\n", initialvalue="CA-V")
1470  if (Channel == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
1471  return
1472  # open file to save data
1473  filename = asksaveasfilename(defaultextension = ".txt", filetypes=[("Text Columns", "*.txt")])
1474  DataFile = open(filename, 'w')
1475  for index in range(len(VBuffA)):
1476  TimePnt = float((index+0.0)/SAMPLErate)
1477  if Channel == "CA-V":
1478  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffA[index]) + '\n')
1479  elif Channel == "CA-I":
1480  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(IBuffA[index]) + '\n')
1481  elif Channel == "CB-V":
1482  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(VBuffB[index]) + '\n')
1483  elif Channel == "CB-I":
1484  DataFile.write( str(TimePnt) + ', ' + str(IBuffB[index]) + '\n')
1485  DataFile.close()

1487 def BReadData():
1488  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, SHOWsamples
1489 
1490  # Read values from CVS file
1491  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".csv", filetypes=[("CSV files", "*.csv")])
1492  try:
1493  CSVFile = open(filename)
1494  dialect = csv.Sniffer().sniff(CSVFile.read(2048))
1495  CSVFile.seek(0)
1496  csv_f = csv.reader(CSVFile, dialect)
1497  VBuffA = []
1498  VBuffB = []
1499  IBuffA = []
1500  IBuffB = []
1501  SHOWsamples = 0
1502  for row in csv_f:
1503  try:
1504  VBuffA.append(float(row[1]))
1505  IBuffA.append(float(row[2]))
1506  VBuffB.append(float(row[3]))
1507  IBuffB.append(float(row[4]))
1508  SHOWsamples = SHOWsamples + 1
1509  except:
1510  print 'skipping non-numeric row'
1511  VBuffA = numpy.array(VBuffA)
1512  IBuffA = numpy.array(IBuffA)
1513  VBuffB = numpy.array(VBuffB)
1514  IBuffB = numpy.array(IBuffB)
1515  CSVFile.close()
1516  UpdateTimeTrace()
1517  except:
1518  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!")

1554  T2VRline = T2Vline # V reference Trace line channel B

1556  T1IRline = T1Iline # I reference Trace line channel A

1560  TMRline = Tmathline # Math reference Trace line
1561  if MuxScreenStatus.get() > 0:
1562  if Show_CBA.get() > 0:
1563  T2VRline = TMAVline # V reference Trace line Mux channel A
1564  if Show_CBB.get() > 0:
1565  TMBRline = TMBVline # V reference Trace line Mux channel B
1566  if Show_CBC.get() > 0:
1567  TMCRline = TMCVline # V reference Trace line Mux channel C
1568  if Show_CBD.get() > 0:
1569  T2IRline = TMDVline # V reference Trace line Mux channel D
1570  if len(TXYline) > 4:
1571  TXYRline = TXYline # XY reference trace line

1595  CalFile.write('CHAIGainEntry.delete(0,END)\n')
1596  CalFile.write('CHAIGainEntry.insert(4, ' + CHAIGainEntry.get() + ')\n')
1597  CalFile.write('CHBIGainEntry.delete(0,END)\n')
1598  CalFile.write('CHBIGainEntry.insert(4, ' + CHBIGainEntry.get() + ')\n')
1599  CalFile.write('CHAIOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)\n')
1600  CalFile.write('CHAIOffsetEntry.insert(4, ' + CHAIOffsetEntry.get() + ')\n')
1601  CalFile.write('CHBIOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)\n')
1602  CalFile.write('CHBIOffsetEntry.insert(4, ' + CHBIOffsetEntry.get() + ')\n')
1603  #
1604  # save channel AC frequency compensation settings
1605  try:
1606  CHA_TC1.set(float(cha_TC1Entry.get()))
1607  CHA_TC2.set(float(cha_TC2Entry.get()))
1608  CHB_TC1.set(float(chb_TC1Entry.get()))
1609  CHB_TC2.set(float(chb_TC2Entry.get()))
1610  CHA_A1.set(float(cha_A1Entry.get()))
1611  CHA_A2.set(float(cha_A2Entry.get()))
1612  CHB_A1.set(float(chb_A1Entry.get()))
1613  CHB_A2.set(float(chb_A2Entry.get()))
1614  except:
1615  donothing()
1616  CalFile.write('CHA_RC_HP.set(' + str(CHA_RC_HP.get()) + ')\n')
1617  CalFile.write('CHB_RC_HP.set(' + str(CHB_RC_HP.get()) + ')\n')
1618  CalFile.write('CHA_TC1.set(' + str(CHA_TC1.get()) + ')\n')
1619  CalFile.write('CHA_TC2.set(' + str(CHA_TC2.get()) + ')\n')
1620  CalFile.write('CHB_TC1.set(' + str(CHB_TC1.get()) + ')\n')
1621  CalFile.write('CHB_TC2.set(' + str(CHB_TC2.get()) + ')\n')
1622  CalFile.write('CHA_A1.set(' + str(CHA_A1.get()) + ')\n')
1623  CalFile.write('CHA_A2.set(' + str(CHA_A2.get()) + ')\n')
1624  CalFile.write('CHB_A1.set(' + str(CHB_A1.get()) + ')\n')
1625  CalFile.write('CHB_A2.set(' + str(CHB_A2.get()) + ')\n')
1626  CalFile.write('cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1627  CalFile.write('cha_TC1Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHA_TC1.get()) + ')\n')
1628  CalFile.write('cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1629  CalFile.write('cha_TC2Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHA_TC2.get()) + ')\n')
1630  CalFile.write('chb_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1631  CalFile.write('chb_TC1Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHB_TC1.get()) + ')\n')
1632  CalFile.write('chb_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1633  CalFile.write('chb_TC2Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHB_TC2.get()) + ')\n')
1634  CalFile.write('cha_A1Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1635  CalFile.write('cha_A1Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHA_A1.get()) + ')\n')
1636  CalFile.write('cha_A2Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1637  CalFile.write('cha_A2Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHA_A2.get()) + ')\n')
1638  CalFile.write('chb_A1Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1639  CalFile.write('chb_A1Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHB_A1.get()) + ')\n')
1640  CalFile.write('chb_A2Entry.delete(0,END)\n')
1641  CalFile.write('chb_A2Entry.insert(4, ' + str(CHB_A2.get()) + ')\n')
1642 
1643  CalFile.close()

1645 def BLoadCal():
1646  global CHAVGainEntry, CHBVGainEntry, CHAVOffsetEntry, CHBVOffsetEntry
1647  global CHAIGainEntry, CHBIGainEntry, CHAIOffsetEntry, CHBIOffsetEntry
1648  global DevID
1649  global CHA_RC_HP, CHB_RC_HP, CHA_TC1, CHA_TC2, CHB_TC1, CHB_TC2
1650  global CHA_A1, CHA_A2, CHB_A1, CHB_A2
1651  global cha_TC1Entry, cha_TC2Entry, chb_TC1Entry, chb_TC2Entry
1652  global cha_A1Entry, cha_A2Entry, chb_A1Entry, chb_A2Entry
1653 
1654  devidstr = DevID[17:31]
1655  filename = devidstr + "_O.cal"
1656  try:
1657  CalFile = open(filename)
1658  for line in CalFile:
1659  exec( line.rstrip() )
1660  CalFile.close()
1661  except:
1662  print "Cal file for this device not found"

1997 def BTrigger50p():
1998  global TgInput, TRIGGERlevel, TRIGGERentry
1999  global MaxV1, MinV1, MaxV2, MinV2
2000  global MaxI1, MinI1, MaxI2, MinI2
2001  # set new trigger level to mid point of waveform
2002  MidV1 = (MaxV1+MinV1)/2
2003  MidV2 = (MaxV2+MinV2)/2
2004  MidI1 = (MaxI1+MinI1)/2
2005  MidI2 = (MaxI2+MinI2)/2
2006  if (TgInput.get() == 0):
2007  DCString = "0.0"
2008  elif (TgInput.get() == 1 ):
2009  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidV1)
2010  elif (TgInput.get() == 2 ):
2011  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidI1)
2012  elif (TgInput.get() == 3 ):
2013  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidV2)
2014  elif (TgInput.get() == 4 ):
2015  DCString = ' {0:.2f} '.format(MidI2)
2016 
2017  TRIGGERlevel = eval(DCString)
2018  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,END)
2019  TRIGGERentry.insert(4, DCString)
2020 
2021  UpdateTimeTrace() # Always Update
2022 
2023 def BTriggerMode():
2024  global TgInput
2025 
2026 # if (TgInput.get() == 0):
2027  # no trigger
2028 # elif (TgInput.get() == 1):
2029  # trigger source set to detector of analog in channels
2030  # auto trigger timeout value
2031 # elif (TgInput.get() == 2):
2032  # trigger source set to detector of analog in channels
2033  # 0 disables auto trigger
2034 
2035 def BTriglevel(event):
2036  global TRIGGERlevel, TRIGGERentry
2037 
2038  # evalute entry string to a numerical value
2039  try:
2040  TRIGGERlevel = float(eval(TRIGGERentry.get()))
2041  except:
2042  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,END)
2043  TRIGGERentry.insert(0, TRIGGERlevel)
2044  # set new trigger level
2045 
2046  UpdateTimeTrace() # Always Update

2257  RUNstatus.set(1)

2271 
2283  BAWGEnab()

2392 def BTime():
2393  global TIMEdiv, TMsb, RUNstatus, Two_X_Sample, ETSDisp, FWRevOne
2394 
2395  try: # get time scale in mSec/div
2396  TIMEdiv = float(eval(TMsb.get()))
2397  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
2398  TIMEdiv = 0.01
2399  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
2400  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
2401  except:
2402  TIMEdiv = 0.5
2403  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
2404  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
2405  # Switch to 2X sampleling if time scale small enough and not runing ETS
2406  if ETSDisp.get() == 0:
2407  Samples_per_div = TIMEdiv * 100.0 # samples per mSec @ base sample rate
2408  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
2409  if Samples_per_div < 20.0:
2410  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
2411  else:
2412  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
2413  SetADC_Mux()
2414  #
2415  if RUNstatus.get() == 2: # Restart if running
2416  RUNstatus.set(4)
2417 
2418  UpdateTimeTrace() # Always Update

2558 def Analog_In():
2559  global RUNstatus, SingleShot, ManualTrigger, TimeDisp, XYDisp, FreqDisp, SpectrumScreenStatus, HWRevOne
2560  global IADisp, IAScreenStatus, CutDC, DevOne, AWGBMode, MuxEnb, BodeScreenStatus, BodeDisp
2561  global MuxScreenStatus, VBuffA, VBuffB, MuxSync, AWGBIOMode
2562  global VmemoryMuxA, VmemoryMuxB, VmemoryMuxC, VmemoryMuxD, MuxChan
2563  global ShowC1_V, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I, SMPfft
2564  global PIO_0, PIO_1, PIO_2, PIO_3, PIO_4, PIO_5, PIO_6, PIO_7
2565  global DCV1, DCV2, MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2
2566  global DCI1, DCI2, MinI1, MaxI1, MinI2, MaxI2
2567  global SV1, SI1, SV2, SI2, SVA_B
2568  global FregPoint, FBins, FStep
2569  # Analog Mux channel measurement variables
2570  global TRACEresetTime, TRACEmodeTime
2571  global VBuffMA, VBuffMB, VBuffMC, VBuffMD, DualMuxMode
2572  global Show_CBA, Show_CBB, Show_CBC, Show_CBD
2573  global DCVMuxA, MinVMuxA, MaxVMuxA, MidVMuxA, PPVMuxA, SVMuxA
2574  global DCVMuxB, MinVMuxB, MaxVMuxB, MidVMuxB, PPVMuxB, SVMuxB
2575  global DCVMuxC, MinVMuxC, MaxVMuxC, MidVMuxC, PPVMuxC, SVMuxC
2576  global DCVMuxD, MinVMuxD, MaxVMuxD, MidVMuxD, PPVMuxD, SVMuxD
2577 
2578  while (True): # Main loop
2579  # RUNstatus = 1 : Open Acquisition
2580  if (RUNstatus.get() == 1) or (RUNstatus.get() == 2):
2581  if TimeDisp.get() > 0 or XYDisp.get() > 0:
2582  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 0:
2583  MuxChan = -1
2584  Analog_Time_In()
2585  else:
2586  if DualMuxMode.get() == 1: # force split I/O mode if dual mux mode set
2587  AWGAIOMode.set(1)
2588  AWGBIOMode.set(1)
2589  ShowC1_V.set(0) # force A voltage trace off
2590  ShowC2_V.set(0) # force B voltage trace off
2591  if HWRevOne == "D" :
2592  # force channel B to always be in High-Z mode for Rev D hardware or if not in split I/O mode
2593  AWGBMode.set(2)
2594  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0: # if not in split I/O mode
2595  ShowC2_I.set(0) # no need to show CH-B current
2596  if MuxEnb.get() == 1:
2597  PIO2 = 0x51
2598  else:
2599  PIO2 = 0x50
2600  if MuxSync.get() == 0:
2601  PIO3 = 0x51
2602  PIO3x = 0x50
2603  else:
2604  PIO3 = 0x50
2605  PIO3x = 0x51
2606  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 0 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2607  TRACEresetTime = True # Clear the memory for averaging
2608  elif TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1:
2609  if TRACEresetTime == True:
2610  TRACEresetTime = False
2611  # Save previous trace in memory for average trace
2612  VmemoryMuxA = VBuffMA
2613  VmemoryMuxB = VBuffMB
2614  VmemoryMuxC = VBuffMC
2615  ImemoryMuxD = VBuffMD
2616  if Show_CBA.get() == 1:
2617  MuxChan = 0
2618  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 0
2619  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 0
2620  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO2, PIO_2, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO enable
2621  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to 1 sync pulse for sweep start
2622  time.sleep(0.002)
2623  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3x, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to return value
2624  Analog_Time_In()
2625  # Average mode 1, add difference / TRACEaverage to arrayif :
2626  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2627  try:
2628  VBuffMA = VmemoryMuxA + (VBuffMA - VmemoryMuxA) / TRACEaverage.get()
2629  except:
2630  # buffer size mismatch so reset memory buffers
2631  VmemoryMuxA = VBuffMA
2632  if Show_CBB.get() == 1:
2633  MuxChan = 1
2634  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 1
2635  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 0
2636  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO2, PIO_2, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 2 to 0
2637  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to sync pulse for sweep start
2638  time.sleep(0.002)
2639  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3x, 3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to return value
2640  Analog_Time_In()
2641  # Average mode 1, add difference / TRACEaverage to arrayif :
2642  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2643  try:
2644  VBuffMB = VmemoryMuxB + (VBuffMB - VmemoryMuxB) / TRACEaverage.get()
2645  except:
2646  # buffer size mismatch so reset memory buffers
2647  VmemoryMuxB = VBuffMB
2648  if Show_CBC.get() == 1:
2649  MuxChan = 2
2650  if DualMuxMode.get() == 1:
2651  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 1
2652  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 0
2653  else:
2654  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 0
2655  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 1
2656  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO2, PIO_2, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 2 to 0
2657  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to sync pulse for sweep start
2658  time.sleep(0.002)
2659  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3x, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to return value
2660  Analog_Time_In()
2661  # Average mode 1, add difference / TRACEaverage to arrayif :
2662  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2663  try:
2664  VBuffMC = VmemoryMuxC + (VBuffMC - VmemoryMuxC) / TRACEaverage.get()
2665  except:
2666  # buffer size mismatch so reset memory buffers
2667  VmemoryMuxC = VBuffMC
2668  if Show_CBD.get() == 1:
2669  MuxChan = 3
2670  if DualMuxMode.get() == 1:
2671  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 0
2672  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x50, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 0
2673  else:
2674  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0 to 1
2675  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, PIO_1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 1 to 1
2676  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO2, PIO_2, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 2 to 0
2677  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to sync pulse for sweep start
2678  time.sleep(0.002)
2679  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, PIO3x, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 3 to return value
2680  Analog_Time_In()
2681  # Average mode 1, add difference / TRACEaverage to arrayif :
2682  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2683  try:

2685  except:
2686  # buffer size mismatch so reset memory buffers
2687  VmemoryMuxD = VBuffMD
2688  if Show_CBA.get() == 0 and Show_CBB.get() == 0 and Show_CBC.get() == 0 and Show_CBD.get() == 0 and ShowC1_V.get() == 1:
2689  Analog_Time_In()
2690  if (FreqDisp.get() > 0 and SpectrumScreenStatus.get() == 1) or (IADisp.get() > 0 and IAScreenStatus.get() == 1) or (BodeDisp.get() > 0 and BodeScreenStatus.get() == 1):
2691  if IADisp.get() > 0 or BodeDisp.get() > 0:
2692  CutDC.set(1) # remove DC portion of waveform
2693  AWGSync.set(1) # Impedance analyzer and Bode plotter must be run in discontinuous mode
2694  if BodeDisp.get() > 0:
2695  if LoopNum.get() <= len(FStep):
2696  FregPoint = FBins[int(FStep[LoopNum.get()-1])] # look up next frequency from list of bins
2697  if FregPoint < 100.0:
2698  SMPfft = 16384
2699  elif FregPoint < 500.0:
2700  SMPfft = 8192
2701  elif FregPoint < 2000.0:
2702  SMPfft = 4096
2703  else:
2704  SMPfft = 2048
2705  if Two_X_Sample.get() > 0 and FregPoint < 2000.0:
2706  SMPfft = SMPfft * 2
2707 
2708  Analog_Freq_In()
2709  elif OhmRunStatus.get() == 1 and OhmDisp.get() == 1:

2714 def Ohm_Analog_In():
2715  global RMode, CHATestVEntry, CHATestREntry, CHA, CHB, devx, OhmA0, OhmA1, discontloop
2716  global AWGAMode, AWGBMode, AWGAShape, AWGSync, AWGBTerm, AWGAOffsetEntry
2717 
2718 # Do input probe Calibration CH1VGain, CH2VGain, CH1VOffset, CH2VOffset
2719  try:
2720  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
2721  except:
2722  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
2723  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
2724  try:
2725  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
2726  except:
2727  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
2728  CHAVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainA)
2729  try:
2730  InOffB = float(eval(CHBVOffsetEntry.get()))
2731  except:
2732  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
2733  CHBVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffB)
2734  try:
2735  InGainB = float(eval(CHBVGainEntry.get()))
2736  except:
2737  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
2738  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)
2739  try:
2740  CurOffA = float(CHAIOffsetEntry.get())
2741  except:
2742  CurOffA = 0.0
2743  try:
2744  CurOffB = float(CHBIOffsetEntry.get())
2745  except:
2746  CurOffB = 0.0
2747  try:
2748  CurGainA = float(CHAIGainEntry.get())
2749  except:
2750  CurGainA = 1.0
2751  try:
2752  CurGainB = float(CHBIGainEntry.get())
2753  except:
2754  CurGainB = 1.0
2755  try:
2756  chatestv = float(eval(CHATestVEntry.get()))
2757  if chatestv > 5.0:
2758  chatestv = 5.0
2759  CHATestVEntry.delete(0,END)
2760  CHATestVEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
2761  except:
2762  CHATestVEntry.delete(0,END)
2763  CHATestVEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
2764  try:
2765  chatestr = float(eval(CHATestREntry.get()))
2766  except:
2767  CHATestREntry.delete(0,END)
2768  CHATestREntry.insert(0, chatestr)
2769  #
2770  DCVA0 = DCVB0 = DCIA0 = DCIB0 = 0.0 # initalize measurment variable
2771  RIN = 1000000 # nominal ALM1000 input resistance is 1 Mohm
2772  # set A and B channels
2773  AWGAMode.set(0) # Set AWG A to SVMI
2774  AWGAShape.set(0) # DC
2775  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
2776  AWGAOffsetEntry.delete(0,"end")
2777  AWGAOffsetEntry.insert(0, chatestv)
2778  if RMode.get() == 0:
2779  AWGBTerm.set(0)
2780  else:
2781  AWGBTerm.set(1)
2782  #
2783  if AWGSync.get() > 0: # awg syn flag set so run in discontinuous mode
2784  if discontloop > 0:
2785  session.flush()
2786  else:
2787  discontloop = 1
2788  time.sleep(0.01)
2789  BAWGEnab()
2790  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(210) # get samples for both channel A and B
2791  # time.sleep(1000.0/SHOWsamples)
2792  else: # running in continuous mode
2793  if session.continuous:
2794  ADsignal1 = devx.read(210, -1, True) # get samples for both channel A and B
2795  #
2796  # get_samples returns a list of values for voltage [0] and current [1]
2797  for index in range(200): # calculate average
2798  DCVA0 += ADsignal1[index+10][0][0] # VAdata # Sum for average CA voltage
2799  DCVB0 += ADsignal1[index+10][1][0] # VBdata # Sum for average CB voltage
2800  DCIA0 += ADsignal1[index+10][0][1] # Sum for average CA current
2801  DCIB0 += ADsignal1[index+10][1][1] # Sum for average CB current
2802 
2803  DCVA0 = DCVA0 / 200.0 # calculate average
2804  DCVB0 = DCVB0 / 200.0 # calculate average
2805  DCIA0 = DCIA0 / 200.0 # calculate average
2806  DCIB0 = DCIB0 / 200.0 # calculate average
2807  DCVA0 = (DCVA0 - InOffA) * InGainA
2808  DCVB0 = (DCVB0 - InOffB) * InGainB
2809  DCIA0 = ((DCIA0*1000) - CurOffA) * CurGainA
2810  DCIB0 = ((DCIB0*1000) - CurOffB) * CurGainB
2811  if RMode.get() == 0: # external resistor
2812  DCM = chatestr * (DCVB0/(DCVA0-DCVB0))
2813  DCR = (DCM * RIN) / (RIN - DCM) # correct for channel B input resistance
2814  else: # use internal 50 ohm resistor
2815  DCR = chatestr * ((DCVA0-DCVB0)/DCVB0)
2816  if DCR < 1000:
2817  OhmString = '{0:.2f} '.format(DCR) + "Ohms "# format with 2 decimal places
2818  else:
2819  OhmString = '{0:.3f} '.format(DCR/1000) + "KOhms " # divide by 1000 and format with 3 decimal places
2820  IAString = "Meas " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(DCIA0) + " mA " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(DCVB0) + " V"
2821  OhmA0.config(text = OhmString) # change displayed value
2822  OhmA1.config(text = IAString) # change displayed value
2823 #
2824  time.sleep(0.1)
2825  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB GND switch to open

2828 def Analog_Time_In():

2836  global RUNstatus, SingleShot, ManualTrigger, TimeDisp, XYDisp, FreqDisp

2866  # get time scale
2867  try:
2868  TIMEdiv = eval(TMsb.get())
2869  except:
2870  TIMEdiv = 0.5
2871  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
2872  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
2873  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
2874  TIMEdiv = 0.01
2875  #
2876  if TRACEmodeTime.get() == 0 and TRACEresetTime == False:
2877  TRACEresetTime = True # Clear the memory for averaging
2878  elif TRACEmodeTime.get() == 1:
2879  if TRACEresetTime == True:
2880  TRACEresetTime = False
2881  # Save previous trace in memory for average trace
2882  VmemoryA = VBuffA
2883  VmemoryB = VBuffB
2884  ImemoryA = IBuffA
2885  ImemoryB = IBuffB
2886 
2887 # Do input divider Calibration CH1VGain, CH2VGain, CH1VOffset, CH2VOffset
2888  try:
2889  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
2890  except:
2891  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
2892  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
2893  try:
2894  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
2895  except:
2896  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)

2900  except:
2901  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
2902  CHBVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffB)

2905  except:
2906  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
2907  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)

2909  CurOffA = float(CHAIOffsetEntry.get()) #/1000.0 # convert to Amps # leave in mA
2910  except:

2912  try:
2913  CurOffB = float(CHBIOffsetEntry.get())#/1000.0 # convert to Amps
2914  except:
2915  CurOffB = 0.0
2916  try:
2917  CurGainA = float(CHAIGainEntry.get())
2918  except:
2919  CurGainA = 1.0
2920  try:
2921  CurGainB = float(CHBIGainEntry.get())
2922  except:
2923  CurGainB = 1.0
2924 #
2925  try:
2926  HoldOff = float(eval(HoldOffentry.get()))
2927  if HoldOff < 0:
2928  HoldOff = 0
2929  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
2930  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
2931  except:
2932  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
2933  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
2934 #
2935  try:
2936  HozPoss = float(eval(HozPossentry.get()))
2937  except:
2938  HozPossentry.delete(0,END)
2939  HozPossentry.insert(0, HozPoss)
2940 
2941  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000 )
2942  hozpos = int(HozPoss * SAMPLErate/1000 )
2943  if hozpos < 0:
2944  hozpos = 0
2945  twoscreens = int(SAMPLErate * 20.0 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0) # number of samples to acquire, 2 screen widths
2946  onescreen = int(twoscreens/2)
2947  if hldn+hozpos > MaxSamples-twoscreens:
2948  hldn = MaxSamples-twoscreens-hozpos
2949  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
2950  HoldOffentry.insert(0, hldn*1000/SAMPLErate)
2951  if ETSDisp.get() > 0:
2952  if TIMEdiv > 0.2:
2953  MaxETSrecord = int(AWGSAMPLErate * 10 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
2954  else:
2955  MaxETSrecord = int(AWGSAMPLErate * 20 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
2956  if (MaxETSrecord*100) > MaxSamples:
2957  MaxETSrecord = MaxSamples / 100
2958  try:
2959  DivX = float(eval(DivXEntry.get()))
2960  if DivX < 2:
2961  DivX = 2
2962  if DivX > 75:
2963  DivX = 75
2964  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
2965  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
2966  except:
2967  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
2968  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
2969  FOff = 25
2970  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
2971  while MulX > MaxETSrecord:
2972  FOff = FOff + 5
2973  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
2974  FOff = 0 - FOff
2975  SRstring = "Rec Len Mul = " + str(MulX) + " samples"
2976  MulXEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
2977  SRstring = "Offset = " + str(FOff) + " samples"
2978  FOffEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
2979  SHOWsamples = int(MulX * 100)
2980  else:
2981  SHOWsamples = twoscreens + hldn + hozpos
2982  if SHOWsamples > MaxSamples: # or a Max of 100,000 samples
2983  SHOWsamples = MaxSamples
2984  if SHOWsamples < MinSamples: # or a Min of 1000 samples
2985  SHOWsamples = MinSamples
2986  if hozpos >= 0:
2987  TRIGGERsample = hldn
2988  else:
2989  TRIGGERsample = abs(hozpos)
2990  TRIGGERsample = TRIGGERsample + hozpos #
2991 # Starting acquisition
2992  if AWGScreenStatus.get() == 1: # don't try to start AWG is AWG screen is closed
2993  if AWGSync.get() > 0: # awg syn flag set so run in discontinuous mode
2994  if discontloop > 0:
2995  session.flush()
2996  else:
2997  discontloop = 1
2998  time.sleep(0.01)
2999  # print "just before awg enable"
3000  BAWGEnab()
3001  # print "just before get samples"
3002  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(SHOWsamples) # get samples for both channel A and B
3003  # waite to finish then return to open termination
3004  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHA 2.5 V switch to open
3005  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHA GND switch to open
3006  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB 2.5 V switch to open
3007  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB GND switch to open
3008  # time.sleep(1000.0/SHOWsamples)
3009  else: # running in continuous mode
3010  if session.continuous:
3011  if MuxScreenStatus.get() > 0:
3012  devx.flush(-1, True)
3013  DummySamples = SHOWsamples*2
3014  if DummySamples < 20000:
3015  DummySamples = 20000
3016  ADsignal1 = devx.read(DummySamples, -1, True) # do dummy read if in analog mux mode
3017  ADsignal1 = devx.read(SHOWsamples, -1, True) # get samples for both channel A and B
3018  #
3019  else:
3020  ADsignal1 = devx.get_samples(SHOWsamples) # , True) # get samples for both channel A and B
3021  # time.sleep(0.01)
3022  # waite to finish then return to open termination
3023  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHA 2.5 V switch to open
3024  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHA GND switch to open
3025  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB 2.5 V switch to open
3026  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set CHB GND switch to open
3027  #
3028  if Alternate_Sweep_Mode.get() == 1 and Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
3029  if ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 0: # VA and VB
3030  VBuffA = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace A
3031  VBuffB = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace B
3032  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 1: # IA and IB
3033  IBuffA = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace A
3034  IBuffB = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace B
3035  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 4: # VA and IA
3036  VBuffA = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace A
3037  IBuffA = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace A
3038  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 5: # VB and IB
3039  VBuffB = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace B
3040  IBuffB = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace B
3041  else:
3042  VBuffA = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace A
3043  IBuffA = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace A
3044  VBuffB = [] # Clear the V Buff array for trace B
3045  IBuffB = [] # Clear the I Buff array for trace B
3046  increment = 1
3047  # SAMPLErate = 200000 #AWGSAMPLErate
3048  if SHOWsamples >= 20000 and DecimateOption.get() > 0:
3049  increment = 2
3050  SAMPLErate = int(AWGSAMPLErate/increment)
3051  if SHOWsamples >= 40000 and DecimateOption.get() > 0:
3052  increment = 4
3053  SAMPLErate = int(AWGSAMPLErate/increment)
3054  index = 0
3055  if SHOWsamples != len(ADsignal1):
3056  SHOWsamples = len(ADsignal1)
3057  while index < SHOWsamples: # build arrays and decimate if needed
3058  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1 and ADC_Mux_Mode.get() < 6:
3059  if ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 0: # VA and VB
3060  VBuffA.append(ADsignal1[index][0][0])
3061  VBuffA.append(ADsignal1[index][1][1])
3062  VBuffB.append(ADsignal1[index][0][1])
3063  VBuffB.append(ADsignal1[index][1][0])
3064  if Alternate_Sweep_Mode.get() == 0:
3065  IBuffA.append(0.0) # fill as a place holder
3066  IBuffA.append(0.0) # fill as a place holder
3067  IBuffB.append(0.0) # fill as a place holder

3473 # High Pass y[n] = alpha * (y[n-1] + x[n] - x[n-1])
3474 # Low Pass y[n] = y[n-1] + (alpha * ((x[n] - x[n-1]))
3475 # All Pass y[n] = alpha * y[n-1] - alpha * (x[n] + x[n-1])
3476 # All Pass y[n] = alpha * (y[n-1] - x[n] - x[n-1])
3477 
3479 def Digital_RC_High_Pass( InBuff, TC1, Gain ):
3480  global SAMPLErate
3481 
3482  OutBuff = []
3483  n = len(InBuff)
3484  Delta = 1.0/SAMPLErate
3485  TC = TC1 * 1.0E-6
3486  Alpha = TC / (TC + Delta)
3487  OutBuff.append(InBuff[1]-InBuff[0]) # set inital sample to derivative (difference of first two samples)
3488  i = 1
3489  while i < n:
3490  OutBuff.append( Alpha * (OutBuff[i-1] + InBuff[i] - InBuff[i-1]) )
3491  i += 1
3492  OutBuff = numpy.array(OutBuff)
3493  OutBuff = InBuff + (OutBuff * Gain)
3494  return OutBuff
3495 
3497 def Digital_RC_Low_Pass( InBuff, TC1, Gain ): # TC1 is in micro seconds
3498  global SAMPLErate
3499 
3500  OutBuff = []
3501  n = len(InBuff)
3502  Delta = 1.0/SAMPLErate
3503  TC = TC1 * 1.0E-6
3504  Alpha = Delta / (TC + Delta)
3505  i = 1
3506  OutBuff.append(Alpha*InBuff[0])
3507  while i < n:
3508  OutBuff.append( OutBuff[i-1] + (Alpha * (InBuff[i] - InBuff[i-1])) )
3509  i += 1
3510  OutBuff = numpy.array(OutBuff)
3511  OutBuff = (OutBuff * Gain)
3512  return OutBuff

3822 def MakeHistogram():
3823  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB, HBuffA, HBuffB
3824  global CH1pdvRange, CHAOffset, CH2pdvRange, CHBOffset
3825  global ShowC1_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I, Xsignal
3826  global DCV1, DCV2, MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2
3827  global DCI1, DCI2, MinI1, MaxI1, MinI2, MaxI2
3828  global VABase, VATop, VBBase, VBTop
3829 
3830  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 or Xsignal.get() == 6:
3831  CHAGridMax = (5 * CH1pdvRange ) + CHAOffset # Calculate CHA Grid Min and Max
3832  CHAGridMin = (-5 * CH1pdvRange ) + CHAOffset
3833  VAMid = (MinV1 + MaxV1)/2 # Find CHA mid value
3834  HBuffA = numpy.histogram(VBuffA, bins=5000, range=[CHAGridMin, CHAGridMax] )
3835  LowerPeak = 0
3836  UpperPeak = 0
3837  b = 0
3838  while (b < 4999):
3839  if HBuffA[0][b] > HBuffA[0][LowerPeak] and HBuffA[1][b] < VAMid:
3840  LowerPeak = b
3841  VABase = HBuffA[1][b]
3842  if HBuffA[0][b] > HBuffA[0][UpperPeak] and HBuffA[1][b] > VAMid:
3843  UpperPeak = b
3844  VATop = HBuffA[1][b]
3845  b = b + 1
3846  if ShowC2_V.get() == 1 or Xsignal.get() == 7:
3847  CHBGridMax = (5 * CH2pdvRange ) + CHBOffset # Calculate CHB Grid Min and Max
3848  CHBGridMin = (-5 * CH2pdvRange ) + CHBOffset
3849  VBMid = (MinV2 + MaxV2)/2 # Find CHB mid value
3850  HBuffB = numpy.histogram(VBuffB, bins=5000, range=[CHBGridMin, CHBGridMax] )
3851  LowerPeak = 0
3852  UpperPeak = 0
3853  b = 0
3854  while (b < 4999):
3855  if HBuffB[0][b] > HBuffB[0][LowerPeak] and HBuffB[1][b] < VBMid:
3856  LowerPeak = b
3857  VBBase = HBuffB[1][b]
3858  if HBuffB[0][b] > HBuffB[0][UpperPeak] and HBuffB[1][b] > VBMid:
3859  UpperPeak = b
3860  VBTop = HBuffB[1][b]
3861  b = b + 1

3871 def FindRisingEdge(Trace1, Trace2):
3872  global MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2, HoldOff, TRIGGERsample, TgInput, LShift
3873  # global VBuffA, VBuffB
3874  global SHOWsamples, SAMPLErate, CHAperiod, CHAfreq, CHBperiod, CHBfreq
3875  global CHAHW, CHALW, CHADCy, CHBHW, CHBLW, CHBDCy, ShowC1_V, ShowC2_V
3876  global CHABphase, CHBADelayR1, CHBADelayR2, CHBADelayF
3877 
3878  anr1 = bnr1 = 0
3879  anf1 = bnf1 = 1
3880  anr2 = bnr2 = 2
3881  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000)
3882  if TgInput.get() > 0: # if triggering right shift arrays to undo trigger left shift
3883  Trace1 = numpy.roll(Trace1, -LShift)
3884  Trace2 = numpy.roll(Trace2, -LShift)
3885  else:
3886  Trace1 = numpy.roll(Trace1, -hldn)
3887  Trace2 = numpy.roll(Trace2, -hldn)
3888  try:
3889  MidV1 = (numpy.amax(Trace1)+numpy.amin(Trace1))/2.0
3890  MidV2 = (numpy.amax(Trace2)+numpy.amin(Trace2))/2.0
3891  except:
3892  MidV1 = (MinV1+MaxV1)/2
3893  MidV2 = (MinV2+MaxV2)/2
3894 # search Trace 1
3895  Arising = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace1) if val >= MidV1 and Trace1[i-1] < MidV1]
3896  Afalling = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace1) if val <= MidV1 and Trace1[i-1] > MidV1]
3897  AIrising = [i - (Trace1[i] - MidV1)/(Trace1[i] - Trace1[i-1]) for i in Arising]
3898  AIfalling = [i - (MidV1 - Trace1[i])/(Trace1[i-1] - Trace1[i]) for i in Afalling]
3899 
3900  CHAfreq = SAMPLErate / numpy.mean(numpy.diff(AIrising))
3901  CHAperiod = (numpy.mean(numpy.diff(AIrising)) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate # time in mSec
3902  if len(Arising) > 0 or len(Afalling) > 0:
3903  if Arising[0] > 0:
3904  try:
3905  anr1 = AIrising[0]
3906  except:
3907  anr1 = 0
3908  try:
3909  anr2 = AIrising[1]
3910  except:
3911  anr2 = SHOWsamples
3912  try:
3913  if AIfalling[0] < AIrising[0]:
3914  anf1 = AIfalling[1]
3915  else:
3916  anf1 = AIfalling[0]
3917  except:
3918  anf1 = 1
3919  else:
3920  try:
3921  anr1 = AIrising[1]
3922  except:
3923  anr1 = 0
3924  try:
3925  anr2 = AIrising[2]
3926  except:
3927  anr2 = SHOWsamples
3928  try:
3929  if AIfalling[1] < AIrising[1]:
3930  anf1 = AIfalling[2]
3931  else:
3932  anf1 = AIfalling[1]
3933  except:
3934  anf1 = 1
3935 # search Trace 2
3936  Brising = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace2) if val >= MidV2 and Trace2[i-1] < MidV2]
3937  Bfalling = [i for (i, val) in enumerate(Trace2) if val <= MidV2 and Trace2[i-1] > MidV2]
3938  BIrising = [i - (Trace2[i] - MidV2)/(Trace2[i] - Trace2[i-1]) for i in Brising]
3939  BIfalling = [i - (MidV2 - Trace2[i])/(Trace2[i-1] - Trace2[i]) for i in Bfalling]
3940 
3941  CHBfreq = SAMPLErate / numpy.mean(numpy.diff(BIrising))
3942  CHBperiod = (numpy.mean(numpy.diff(BIrising)) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate # time in mSec
3943  if len(Brising) > 0 or len(Bfalling) > 0:
3944  if Brising[0] > 0:
3945  try:
3946  bnr1 = BIrising[0]
3947  except:
3948  bnr1 = 0
3949  try:
3950  bnr2 = BIrising[1]
3951  except:
3952  bnr2 = SHOWsamples
3953  try:
3954  if BIfalling[0] < BIrising[0]:
3955  bnf1 = BIfalling[1]
3956  else:
3957  bnf1 = BIfalling[0]
3958  except:
3959  bnf1 = 1
3960  else:
3961  try:
3962  bnr1 = BIrising[1]
3963  except:
3964  bnr1 = 0
3965  try:
3966  bnr2 = BIrising[2]
3967  except:
3968  bnr2 = SHOWsamples
3969  try:
3970  if BIfalling[1] < BIrising[1]:
3971  bnf1 = BIfalling[2]
3972  else:
3973  bnf1 = BIfalling[1]
3974  except:
3975  bnf1 = 1
3976  #
3977  CHAHW = float(((anf1 - anr1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
3978  CHALW = float(((anr2 - anf1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
3979  CHADCy = float(anf1 - anr1) / float(anr2 - anr1) * 100.0 # in percent
3980  CHBHW = float(((bnf1 - bnr1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
3981  CHBLW = float(((bnr2 - bnf1) * 1000.0) / SAMPLErate)
3982  CHBDCy = float(bnf1 - bnr1) / float(bnr2 - bnr1) * 100.0 # in percent
3983 #
3984  if bnr1 > anr1:
3985  CHBADelayR1 = float((bnr1 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
3986  else:
3987  CHBADelayR1 = float((bnr2 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
3988  CHBADelayR2 = float((bnr2 - anr2) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
3989  CHBADelayF = float((bnf1 - anf1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate)
3990  try:
3991  CHABphase = 360.0*(float((bnr1 - anr1) * 1000.0 / SAMPLErate))/CHAperiod
3992  except:
3993  CHABphase = 0.0
3994  if CHABphase < 0.0:
3995  CHABphase = CHABphase + 360.0
3996 
3997 def ReInterploateTrigger(TrgBuff):
3998  global DX, TRIGGERsample, TRIGGERlevel
3999 
4000  DX = 0
4001  n = TRIGGERsample
4002  DY = TrgBuff[int(n)] - TrgBuff[int(n+1)]
4003  if DY != 0.0:
4004  DX = (TRIGGERlevel - TrgBuff[int(n+1)])/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
4005  else:
4006  DX = 0
4007 
4008 def FindTriggerSample(TrgBuff): # find trigger time sample point of passed waveform array
4009  global AutoLevel, TgInput, TRIGGERlevel, TRIGGERentry, DX, SAMPLErate, Is_Triggered
4010  global HoldOffentry, HozPossentry, TRIGGERsample, TRACEsize, HozPoss, hozpos
4011 
4012  # Set the TRACEsize variable
4013  TRACEsize = SHOWsamples # Set the trace length
4014  DX = 0
4015  Is_Triggered = 0
4016  try:
4017  TrgMin = numpy.amin(TrgBuff)
4018  except:
4019  TrgMin = 0.0
4020  try:
4021  TrgMax = numpy.amax(TrgBuff)
4022  except:
4023  TrgMax = 0.0
4024 # Find trigger sample
4025  try:
4026  if AutoLevel.get() == 1:
4027  TRIGGERlevel = (TrgMin + TrgMax)/2
4028  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,"end")
4029  TRIGGERentry.insert(0, ' {0:.4f} '.format(TRIGGERlevel))
4030  else:
4031  TRIGGERlevel = eval(TRIGGERentry.get())
4032  except:
4033  TRIGGERentry.delete(0,END)
4034  TRIGGERentry.insert(0, TRIGGERlevel)
4035 # Start from first sample after HoldOff
4036  try:
4037  HoldOff = float(eval(HoldOffentry.get()))
4038  if HoldOff < 0:
4039  HoldOff = 0
4040  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
4041  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
4042  except:
4043  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
4044  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
4045 # slide trace left right by HozPoss
4046  try:
4047  HozPoss = float(eval(HozPossentry.get()))
4048  except:
4049  HozPossentry.delete(0,END)
4050  HozPossentry.insert(0, HozPoss)
4051 
4052  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000)
4053  hozpos = int(HozPoss * SAMPLErate/1000)
4054  if hozpos >= 0:
4055  TRIGGERsample = hldn
4056  else:
4057  TRIGGERsample = abs(hozpos)
4058 #
4059  Nmax = int(TRACEsize / 1.5) # first 2/3 of data set
4060  DX = 0
4061  n = TRIGGERsample
4062  TRIGGERlevel2 = 0.99 * TRIGGERlevel # Hysteresis to avoid triggering on noise
4063  if TRIGGERlevel2 < TrgMin:
4064  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMin
4065  if TRIGGERlevel2 > TrgMax:
4066  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMax
4067  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4068  Prev = ChInput
4069  while ( ChInput >= TRIGGERlevel2) and n < Nmax:
4070  n = n + 1
4071  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4072  while (ChInput <= TRIGGERlevel) and n < Nmax:
4073  Prev = ChInput
4074  n = n + 1
4075  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4076  DY = ChInput - Prev
4077  if DY != 0.0:
4078  DX = (TRIGGERlevel - Prev)/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
4079  else:
4080  DX = 0
4081  if TgEdge.get() == 1:
4082  TRIGGERlevel2 = 1.01 * TRIGGERlevel
4083  if TRIGGERlevel2 < TrgMin:
4084  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMin
4085  if TRIGGERlevel2 > TrgMax:
4086  TRIGGERlevel2 = TrgMax
4087  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4088  Prev = ChInput
4089  while (ChInput <= TRIGGERlevel2) and n < Nmax:
4090  n = n + 1
4091  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4092  while (ChInput >= TRIGGERlevel) and n < Nmax:
4093  Prev = ChInput
4094  n = n + 1
4095  ChInput = TrgBuff[int(n)]
4096  DY = Prev - ChInput
4097  try:
4098  DX = (Prev - TRIGGERlevel)/DY # calculate interpolated trigger point
4099  except:
4100  DX = 0
4101 
4102 # check to insure trigger point is in bounds
4103  if n < Nmax:
4104  TRIGGERsample = n - 1
4105  Is_Triggered = 1
4106  elif n > Nmax: # Didn't find edge in first 2/3 of data set
4107  TRIGGERsample = 1 + hldn # reset to begining
4108  Is_Triggered = 0
4109  if DX > 1:
4110  DX = 1 # never more than 100% of a sample period
4111  elif DX < 0:
4112  DX = 0 # never less than 0% of a sample period
4113  if math.isnan(DX):
4114  DX = 0
4115  TRIGGERsample = TRIGGERsample + hozpos
4116

4359  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, PIO_3, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 0
4360  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, PIO_7, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set PIO 4

4414 def MakeTimeTrace():
4415  global VBuffA, VBuffB, IBuffA, IBuffB
4416  global VBuffMA, VBuffMB, VBuffMC, VBuffMD, MuxScreenStatus
4417  global VmemoryA, VmemoryB, ImemoryA, ImemoryB
4418  global VmemoryMuxA, VmemoryMuxB, VmemoryMuxC, VmemoryMuxD

4421  global T1Vline, T2Vline, T1Iline, T2Iline
4422  global TMAVline, TMBVline, TMCVline, TMDVline
4423  global Tmathline, TMXline, TMYline
4424  global MathString, MathAxis, MathXString, MathYString, MathXAxis, MathYAxis

4430  global Show_CBA, Show_CBB, Show_CBC, Show_CBD

4433  global AutoCenterA, AutoCenterB
4434  global CHAsb, CHBsb, CHAOffset, CHBOffset, CHAIsb, CHBIsb, CHAIOffset, CHBIOffset
4435  global TMpdiv # Array with time / div values in ms
4436  global TMsb # Time per div spin box variable
4437  global TIMEdiv # current spin box value
4438  global SAMPLErate, SCstart, Two_X_Sample
4439  global TRIGGERsample, TRACEsize, DX
4440  global TRIGGERlevel, TRIGGERentry, AutoLevel
4441  global InOffA, InGainA, InOffB, InGainB
4442  global DCV1, DCV2, MinV1, MaxV1, MinV2, MaxV2
4443  global DCI1, DCI2, MinI1, MaxI1, MinI2, MaxI2
4444  global CHAVGainEntry, CHBVGainEntry, CHAVOffsetEntry, CHBVOffsetEntry
4445  global CHAVPosEntry, CHAIPosEntry, CHAVPosEntry, CHBIPosEntry
4446  global CHAIGainEntry, CHBIGainEntry, CHAIOffsetEntry, CHBIOffsetEntry
4447  global CHB_Asb, CHB_APosEntry, CHB_Bsb, CHB_BPosEntry
4448  global CHB_Csb, CHB_CPosEntry, CHB_Dsb, CHB_DPosEntry
4449  global HozPoss, HozPossentry
4450 
4451  # Set the TRACEsize variable
4452  if len(VBuffA) < 100:
4453  return
4454  TRACEsize = SHOWsamples # Set the trace length
4455  SCstart = 0
4456  ylo = 0.0
4457  xlo = 0.0
4458  Ymin = Y0T # Minimum position of time grid (top)
4459  Ymax = Y0T + GRH # Maximum position of time grid (bottom)
4460  Xmin = X0L # Minimum position of time grid (left)
4461  Xmax = X0L + GRW # Maximum position of time grid (right)
4462  # get time scale
4463  try:
4464  TIMEdiv = float(eval(TMsb.get()))
4465  except:
4466  TIMEdiv = 0.5
4467  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
4468  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
4469  # prevent divide by zero error
4470  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
4471  TIMEdiv = 0.01
4472  # Check for Auto Centering
4473  if AutoCenterA.get() > 0:
4474  CHAOffset = DCV1
4475  CHAVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4476  CHAVPosEntry.insert(0, ' {0:.2f} '.format(CHAOffset))
4477  if AutoCenterB.get() > 0:
4478  CHBOffset = DCV2
4479  CHBVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4480  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, ' {0:.2f} '.format(CHBOffset))
4481  # get the vertical ranges
4482  try:
4483  CH1pdvRange = float(eval(CHAsb.get()))
4484  except:
4485  CHAsb.delete(0,END)
4486  CHAsb.insert(0, CH1vpdvRange)
4487  try:
4488  CH2pdvRange = float(eval(CHBsb.get()))
4489  except:
4490  CHBsb.delete(0,END)
4491  CHBsb.insert(0, CH2vpdvRange)
4492  try:
4493  CH1IpdvRange = float(eval(CHAIsb.get()))
4494  except:
4495  CHAIsb.delete(0,END)
4496  CHAIsb.insert(0, CH1IpdvRange)
4497  try:
4498  CH2IpdvRange = float(eval(CHBIsb.get()))
4499  except:
4500  CHBIsb.delete(0,END)
4501  CHBIsb.insert(0, CH2IpdvRange)
4502  # get the vertical offsets
4503  try:
4504  CHAOffset = float(eval(CHAVPosEntry.get()))
4505  except:
4506  CHAVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4507  CHAVPosEntry.insert(0, CHAOffset)
4508  try:
4509  CHAIOffset = float(eval(CHAIPosEntry.get()))
4510  except:
4511  CHAIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4512  CHAIPosEntry.insert(0, CHAIOffset)
4513  try:
4514  CHBOffset = float(eval(CHBVPosEntry.get()))
4515  except:
4516  CHBVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4517  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, CHBOffset)
4518  try:
4519  CHBIOffset = float(eval(CHBIPosEntry.get()))
4520  except:
4521  CHBIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4522  CHBIPosEntry.insert(0, CHBIOffset)
4523  # prevent divide by zero error
4524  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
4525  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
4526  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
4527  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
4528  if CH1IpdvRange < 0.1:
4529  CH1IpdvRange = 0.1
4530  if CH2IpdvRange < 0.1:
4531  CH2IpdvRange = 0.1
4532 #
4533  try:
4534  HoldOff = float(eval(HoldOffentry.get()))
4535  if HoldOff < 0:
4536  HoldOff = 0
4537  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
4538  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
4539  except:
4540  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
4541  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
4542 #
4543  try:
4544  HozPoss = float(eval(HozPossentry.get()))
4545  except:
4546  HozPossentry.delete(0,END)
4547  HozPossentry.insert(0, HozPoss)
4548 #
4549  hldn = int(HoldOff * SAMPLErate/1000 )
4550  hozpos = int(HozPoss * SAMPLErate/1000 )
4551  if hozpos < 0:
4552  hozpos = 0
4553  # drawing the traces
4554  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
4555  T1Vline = [] # Trace line channel A V
4556  T2Vline = [] # Trace line channel B V
4557  T1Iline = []
4558  T2Iline = []
4559  TMAVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel A
4560  TMBVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel B
4561  TMCVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel C
4562  TMDVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel D
4563  Tmathline = [] # math trce line
4564  return()
4565 
4566  try:
4567  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
4568  except:
4569  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
4570  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
4571  try:
4572  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
4573  except:
4574  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
4575  CHAVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainA)
4576  try:
4577  InOffB = float(eval(CHBVOffsetEntry.get()))
4578  except:
4579  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
4580  CHBVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffB)
4581  try:
4582  InGainB = float(eval(CHBVGainEntry.get()))
4583  except:
4584  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
4585  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)
4586 #
4587  try:
4588  CurOffA = float(CHAIOffsetEntry.get()) # leave in mA
4589  except:
4590  CurOffA = 0.0
4591  try:
4592  CurOffB = float(CHBIOffsetEntry.get()) # leave in mA
4593  except:
4594  CurOffB = 0.0
4595  try:
4596  CurGainA = float(CHAIGainEntry.get())
4597  except:
4598  CurGainA = 1.0
4599  try:
4600  CurGainB = float(CHBIGainEntry.get())
4601  except:
4602  CurGainB = 1.0
4603 
4604  # set and/or corrected for in range
4605  if TgInput.get() > 0:
4606  SCmin = int(-1 * TRIGGERsample)
4607  SCmax = int(TRACEsize - TRIGGERsample - 0)
4608  else:
4609  SCmin = 0 # hldn
4610  SCmax = TRACEsize - 1
4611  if SCstart < SCmin: # No reading before start of array
4612  SCstart = SCmin
4613  if SCstart > SCmax: # No reading after end of array
4614  SCstart = SCmax
4615 
4616  # Make Trace lines etc.
4617 
4618  Yconv1 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Vertical Conversion factors from samples to screen points
4619  Yconv2 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
4620  YIconv1 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
4621  YIconv2 = float(GRH/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
4622  Xconv1 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Horizontal Conversion factors from samples to screen points
4623  Xconv2 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
4624  XIconv1 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
4625  XIconv2 = float(GRW/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
4626  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1: # if using analog Mux set up axis controls
4627  try:
4628  CHMApdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Asb.get()))
4629  except:
4630  CHB_Asb.delete(0,END)
4631  CHB_Asb.insert(0, CHMApdvRange)
4632  try:
4633  CHMBpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Bsb.get()))
4634  except:
4635  CHB_Bsb.delete(0,END)
4636  CHB_Bsb.insert(0, CHMBpdvRange)
4637  try:
4638  CHMCpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Csb.get()))
4639  except:
4640  CHB_Csb.delete(0,END)
4641  CHB_Csb.insert(0, CHMCpdvRange)
4642  try:
4643  CHMDpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Dsb.get()))
4644  except:
4645  CHB_Dsb.delete(0,END)
4646  CHB_Dsb.insert(0, CHMDpdvRange)
4647  YconvMA = float(GRH/10.0) / CHMApdvRange
4648  YconvMB = float(GRH/10.0) / CHMBpdvRange
4649  YconvMC = float(GRH/10.0) / CHMCpdvRange
4650  YconvMD = float(GRH/10.0) / CHMDpdvRange
4651  try:
4652  CHBAOffset = float(eval(CHB_APosEntry.get()))
4653  except:
4654  CHB_APosEntry.delete(0,END)
4655  CHB_APosEntry.insert(0, CHBAOffset)
4656  try:
4657  CHBBOffset = float(eval(CHB_BPosEntry.get()))
4658  except:
4659  CHB_BPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4660  CHB_BPosEntry.insert(0, CHBBOffset)
4661  try:
4662  CHBCOffset = float(eval(CHB_CPosEntry.get()))
4663  except:
4664  CHB_CPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4665  CHB_CPosEntry.insert(0, CHBCOffset)
4666  try:
4667  CHBDOffset = float(eval(CHB_DPosEntry.get()))
4668  except:
4669  CHB_DPosEntry.delete(0,END)
4670  CHB_DPosEntry.insert(0, CHBDOffset)
4671  if MathAxis == "V-A":
4672  YconvM = Yconv1
4673  CHMOffset = CHAOffset
4674  elif MathAxis == "V-B":
4675  YconvM = Yconv2
4676  CHMOffset = CHBOffset
4677  elif MathAxis == "I-A":
4678  YconvM = YIconv1
4679  CHMOffset = CHAIOffset
4680  elif MathAxis == "I-B":
4681  YconvM = YIconv2
4682  CHMOffset = CHBIOffset
4683  else:
4684  YconvM = Yconv1
4685  CHMOffset = CHAOffset
4686 # include ploting X and Y math formulas vs time
4687  if MathYAxis == "V-A":
4688  YconvMxy = Yconv1
4689  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
4690  elif MathYAxis == "V-B":
4691  YconvMxy = Yconv2
4692  CHMYOffset = CHBOffset
4693  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":
4694  YconvMxy = YIconv1
4695  CHMYOffset = CHAIOffset
4696  elif MathYAxis == "I-B":
4697  YconvMxy = YIconv2
4698  CHMYOffset = CHBIOffset
4699  else:
4700  YconvMxy = Yconv1
4701  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
4702 #
4703  if MathXAxis == "V-A":
4704  XconvMxy = Yconv1
4705  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
4706  elif MathXAxis == "V-B":
4707  XconvMxy = Yconv2
4708  CHMXOffset = CHBOffset
4709  elif MathXAxis == "I-A":
4710  XconvMxy = YIconv1
4711  CHMXOffset = CHAIOffset
4712  elif MathXAxis == "I-B":
4713  XconvMxy = YIconv2
4714  CHMXOffset = CHBIOffset
4715  else:
4716  XconvMxy = Yconv1
4717  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
4718 #
4719  c1 = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T # fixed correction channel A
4720  c2 = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T # fixed correction channel B
4721 
4722  DISsamples = SAMPLErate * 10.0 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0 # number of samples to display
4723  T1Vline = [] # V Trace line channel A
4724  T2Vline = [] # V Trace line channel B
4725  T1Iline = [] # I Trace line channel A
4726  T2Iline = [] # I Trace line channel B
4727  TMAVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel A
4728  TMBVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel B
4729  TMCVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel C
4730  TMDVline = [] # V Trace line Mux channel D
4731  Tmathline = [] # math trce line
4732  TMXline = [] # X math Trace line
4733  TMYline = [] # Y math Trace line
4734  if len(VBuffA) < 4 and len(VBuffB) < 4 and len(IBuffA) < 4 and len(IBuffB) < 4:
4735  return
4736  t = int(SCstart + TRIGGERsample) # - (TriggerPos * SAMPLErate) # t = Start sample in trace
4737  if t < 0:
4738  t = 0
4739  x = 0 # Horizontal screen pixel
4740 #
4741  ypv1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
4742  ypi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (IBuffA[t] - CHAIOffset))
4743  ypv2 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
4744  ypi2 = int(c1 - YIconv2 * (IBuffB[t] - CHBIOffset))
4745  DvY1 = DvY2 = DiY1 = DiY2 = 0
4746 #
4747  if (DISsamples <= GRW):
4748  Xstep = GRW / DISsamples
4749  if AWGBMode.get() == 2 and Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
4750  xa = int((Xstep/-2.5) - (Xstep*DX))
4751  else:
4752  xa = 0 - int(Xstep*DX) # adjust start pixel for interpolated trigger point
4753  x = 0 - int(Xstep*DX)
4754  Tstep = 1
4755  x1 = 0 # x position of trace line
4756  xa1 = 0
4757  y1 = 0.0 # y position of trace line
4758  ypv1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
4759  ytemp = IBuffA[t]
4760  ypi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (ytemp - CHAIOffset))
4761  ypv2 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
4762  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1:
4763  if len(VBuffMA) > 4:
4764  ypvma = int(c2 - YconvMA * (VBuffMA[t] - CHBAOffset))
4765  if len(VBuffMB) > 4:
4766  ypvmb = int(c2 - YconvMB * (VBuffMB[t] - CHBBOffset))
4767  if len(VBuffMC) > 4:
4768  ypvmc = int(c2 - YconvMC * (VBuffMC[t] - CHBCOffset))
4769  if len(VBuffMD) > 4:
4770  ypvmd = int(c2 - YconvMD * (VBuffMD[t] - CHBDOffset))
4771  ytemp = IBuffB[t]
4772  ypi2 = int(c1 - YIconv2 * (ytemp - CHBIOffset))
4773  ypm = ypmx = ypmy = GRH / 2.0 + Y0T
4774  if TgInput.get() == 0:
4775  Xlimit = GRW
4776  else:
4777  Xlimit = GRW+Xstep
4778  while x <= Xlimit:
4779  if t < TRACEsize:
4780  xa1 = xa + X0L
4781  x1 = x + X0L
4782  y1 = int(c1 - Yconv1 * (VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset))
4783  ytemp = IBuffA[t]
4784  yi1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (ytemp - CHAIOffset))
4785 
4786  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
4787  y1 = Ymin
4788  if y1 > Ymax:
4789  y1 = Ymax
4790  if yi1 < Ymin:
4791  yi1 = Ymin
4792  if yi1 > Ymax:
4793  yi1 = Ymax
4794  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 :
4795  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
4796  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
4797  T1Vline.append(int(ypv1))
4798  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
4799  T1Vline.append(int(y1))
4800  else:
4801  T1Vline.append(int(xa1))
4802  T1Vline.append(int(y1))
4803  DvY1 = ypv1 - y1
4804  ypv1 = y1
4805  if ShowC1_I.get() == 1:
4806  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
4807  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
4808  T1Iline.append(int(ypi1))
4809  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
4810  T1Iline.append(int(yi1))
4811  else:
4812  T1Iline.append(int(xa1))
4813  T1Iline.append(int(yi1))
4814  DiY1 = ypi1 - yi1
4815  ypi1 = yi1
4816  if ShowC2_V.get() == 1:
4817  y1 = int(c2 - Yconv2 * (VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset))
4818  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
4819  y1 = Ymin
4820  if y1 > Ymax:
4821  y1 = Ymax
4822  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
4823  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
4824  T2Vline.append(int(ypv2))
4825  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
4826  T2Vline.append(int(y1))
4827  else:
4828  T2Vline.append(int(x1))
4829  T2Vline.append(int(y1))
4830  DvY2 = ypv2 - y1
4831  ypv2 = y1
4832  if Show_CBA.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMA)>4:
4833  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMA * (VBuffMA[t] - CHBAOffset))
4834  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
4835  y1 = Ymin
4836  if y1 > Ymax:
4837  y1 = Ymax
4838  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
4839  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
4840  TMAVline.append(int(ypvma))
4841  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
4842  TMAVline.append(int(y1))
4843  else:
4844  TMAVline.append(int(x1))
4845  TMAVline.append(int(y1))
4846  ypvma = y1
4847  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
4848  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
4849  MouseMuxA = ypvma - (y1 - ypvma) * (Xfine/Xstep)
4850  if Show_CBB.get() == 1 and MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1 and len(VBuffMB)>4:
4851  y1 = int(c2 - YconvMB * (VBuffMB[t] - CHBBOffset))
4852  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
4853  y1 = Ymin
4854  if y1 > Ymax:
4855  y1 = Ymax
4856  if ZOHold.get() == 1:
4857  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
4858  TMBVline.append(int(ypvmb))
4859  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
4860  TMBVline.append(int(y1))
4861  else:
4862  TMBVline.append(int(x1))
4863  TMBVline.append(int(y1))
4864  ypvmb = y1
4865  if (MouseX - X0L) >= x and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + Xstep):
4866  Xfine = MouseX - X0L - x
4867  MouseMuxB = ypvmb - (y1 - ypvmb) * (Xfine/Xstep)

5388  except:
5389  RUNstatus.set(0)
5390  x = GRW + 1
5391 
5392  if y1 < Ymin: # clip waveform if going off grid
5393  y1 = Ymin
5394  if y1 > Ymax:
5395  y1 = Ymax

5397  TMXline.append(int(x1))
5398  TMXline.append(int(ypmx))

5400  TMXline.append(int(y1))
5401  else: # connet the dots with single line

5403  TMXline.append(int(y1))

5405  if Show_MathY.get() > 0:
5406  try:
5407  MathResult = eval(MathYString)
5408  MathResult = MathResult - CHMYOffset
5409  y1 = int(c1 - YconvMxy * MathResult)
5410  except:
5411  RUNstatus.set(0)
5412  x = GRW + 1
5413

5415  y1 = Ymin
5416  if y1 > Ymax:
5417  y1 = Ymax
5418  if ZOHold.get() == 1: # connet the dots with stair step

5422  TMYline.append(int(y1))
5423  else: # connet the dots with single line
5424  TMYline.append(int(x1))
5425  TMYline.append(int(y1))

5427  ft = ft + Tstep
5428  if (MouseX - X0L) == x: # > (x - 1) and (MouseX - X0L) < (x + 1):
5429  MouseCAV = ypv1
5430  MouseCAI = ypi1
5431  MouseCBV = ypv2
5432  MouseCBI = ypi2
5433  t = int(ft)
5434  x = x + Xstep
5435

5437  Triggerline = [] # Trigger pointer
5438  Triggersymbol = [] # Trigger symbol
5439  if TgInput.get() > 0:
5440  if TgInput.get() == 1 : # triggering on CA-V
5441  x1 = X0L
5442  ytemp = Yconv1 * (float(TRIGGERlevel)-CHAOffset) # / InGainA
5443  y1 = int(c1 - ytemp)
5444  elif TgInput.get() == 2: # triggering on CA-I
5445  x1 = X0L+GRW
5446  y1 = int(c1 - YIconv1 * (float(TRIGGERlevel) - CHAIOffset))
5447  elif TgInput.get() == 3: # triggering on CB-V
5448  x1 = X0L
5449  ytemp = Yconv2 * (float(TRIGGERlevel)-CHBOffset) # / InGainB
5450  y1 = int(c2 - ytemp)
5451  elif TgInput.get() == 4: # triggering on CB-I
5452  x1 = X0L+GRW
5453  y1 = int(c2 - YIconv2 * (float(TRIGGERlevel) - CHBIOffset))
5454 
5455  if (y1 < Ymin):
5456  y1 = Ymin
5457  if (y1 > Ymax):
5458  y1 = Ymax
5459  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
5460  Triggerline.append(int(y1+5))
5461  Triggerline.append(int(x1+5))
5462  Triggerline.append(int(y1))
5463  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
5464  Triggerline.append(int(y1-5))
5465  Triggerline.append(int(x1-5))
5466  Triggerline.append(int(y1+5))
5467  x1 = X0L + (GRW/2)
5468  if TgEdge.get() == 0: # draw rising edge symbol
5469  y1 = -3
5470  y2 = -13
5471  else:
5472  y1 = -13
5473  y2 = -3
5474  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1-10))
5475  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y1))
5476  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1))
5477  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y1))
5478  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1))
5479  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y2))
5480  Triggersymbol.append(int(x1+10))
5481  Triggersymbol.append(int(Ymin+y2))

5483 def MakeXYTrace():

5510  # Set the TRACEsize variable

5514  SCstart = 0
5515  ylo = 0.0
5516  xlo = 0.0
5517  # get the vertical ranges
5518  try:

5520  except:

5522  CHAsbxy.insert(0, CH1vpdvRange)
5523  try:
5524  CH2pdvRange = float(eval(CHBsbxy.get()))
5525  except:

5527  CHBsbxy.insert(0, CH2vpdvRange)

5530  except:
5531  CHAIsbxy.delete(0,END)
5532  CHAIsbxy.insert(0, CH1IpdvRange)
5533  try:
5534  CH2IpdvRange = float(eval(CHBIsbxy.get()))
5535  except:
5536  CHBIsbxy.delete(0,END)
5537  CHBIsbxy.insert(0, CH2IpdvRange)
5538  # get the vertical offsets
5539  try:

5541  except:

5546  except:

5551  except:

5556  except:
5557  CHBIPosEntryxy.delete(0,END)
5558  CHBIPosEntryxy.insert(0, CHBIOffset)
5559  # prevent divide by zero error
5560  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
5561  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
5562  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
5563  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
5564  if CH1IpdvRange < 0.1:
5565  CH1IpdvRange = 0.1
5566  if CH2IpdvRange < 0.1:
5567  CH2IpdvRange = 0.1
5568  #
5569  Yconv1 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Vertical Conversion factors from samples to screen points
5570  Yconv2 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
5571  YIconv1 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
5572  YIconv2 = float(GRHXY/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
5573  Xconv1 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH1pdvRange # Horizontal Conversion factors from samples to screen points
5574  Xconv2 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH2pdvRange
5575  XIconv1 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH1IpdvRange
5576  XIconv2 = float(GRWXY/10.0) / CH2IpdvRange
5577 
5578  if MathYAxis == "V-A":
5579  YconvMxy = Yconv1
5580  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
5581  elif MathYAxis == "V-B":
5582  YconvMxy = Yconv2
5583  CHMYOffset = CHBOffset
5584  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":
5585  YconvMxy = YIconv1
5586  CHMYOffset = CHAIOffset
5587  elif MathYAxis == "I-B":
5588  YconvMxy = YIconv2
5589  CHMYOffset = CHBIOffset
5590  else:
5591  YconvMxy = Yconv1
5592  CHMYOffset = CHAOffset
5593  if MathXAxis == "V-A":
5594  XconvMxy = Xconv1
5595  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
5596  elif MathXAxis == "V-B":
5597  XconvMxy = Xconv2
5598  CHMXOffset = CHBOffset
5599  elif MathYAxis == "I-A":
5600  XconvMxy = XIconv1
5601  CHMXOffset = CHAIOffset
5602  elif MathXAxis == "I-B":
5603  XconvMxy = XIconv2
5604  CHMXOffset = CHBIOffset
5605  else:
5606  XconvMxy = Xconv1
5607  CHMXOffset = CHAOffset
5608  # draw an X/Y plot
5609  TXYline = [] # XY Trace line
5610  t = int(TRIGGERsample) # skip over sampled before hold off time and trigger point
5611  c1 = GRHXY / 2.0 + Y0TXY # fixed correction channel A
5612  c2 = GRWXY / 2.0 + X0LXY # Hor correction factor
5613  while (t < TRACEsize):
5614  if (Xsignal.get() == 3 and Ysignal.get() == 1): # mode CAV/CBV
5615  ylo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5616  xlo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5617  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv1 * ylo)
5618  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5619  elif (Xsignal.get() == 1 and Ysignal.get() == 3): # mode CBV/CAV
5620  ylo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5621  xlo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5622  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)
5623  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5624  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 3): # mode CBV/Math
5625  if ( MathTrace.get() == 2): # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
5626  ylo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5627  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)
5628  xlo = VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset
5629  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5630  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 4): # mode CBI/Math
5631  if ( MathTrace.get() == 2): # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
5632  ylo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
5633  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv2 * ylo)
5634  xlo = VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset
5635  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5636  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 2): # mode CAI/Math
5637  if MathTrace.get() == 3: # plot difference of CB-V and CA-V
5638  ylo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5639  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv1 * ylo)
5640  xlo = VBuffB[t] - VBuffA[t] - CHBOffset
5641  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5642  elif (Xsignal.get() == 3 and Ysignal.get() == 5): # mode Math/CBV
5643  if MathTrace.get() == 2: # plot difference of CA-V and CB-V
5644  ylo = VBuffA[t] - VBuffB[t] - CHAOffset
5645  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv1 * ylo)
5646  xlo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5647  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5648  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 1): # mode CAV/Math
5649  if MathTrace.get() == 3: # plot difference of CB-V and CA-V
5650  ylo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5651  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv1 * ylo)
5652  xlo = VBuffB[t] - VBuffA[t] - CHBOffset
5653  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5654  elif (Xsignal.get() == 1 and Ysignal.get() == 5): # mode Math/CAV
5655  if MathTrace.get() == 3: # plot difference of CB-V and CA-V
5656  ylo = VBuffB[t] - VBuffA[t] - CHBOffset
5657  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)
5658  xlo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5659  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5660  elif (Xsignal.get() == 1 and Ysignal.get() == 2): # mode CAI/CAV
5661  ylo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5662  xlo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5663  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv1 * ylo)
5664  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5665  elif (Xsignal.get() == 3 and Ysignal.get() == 2): # mode CAI/CBV
5666  ylo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5667  xlo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5668  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv1 * ylo)
5669  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5670  elif (Xsignal.get() == 2 and Ysignal.get() == 1): # mode CAV/CAI
5671  ylo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5672  xlo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5673  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv1 * ylo)
5674  xlo = int(c2 + XIconv1 * xlo)
5675  elif (Xsignal.get() == 2 and Ysignal.get() == 3): # mode CBV/CAI
5676  ylo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5677  xlo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5678  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)
5679  xlo = int(c2 + XIconv1 * xlo)
5680  elif (Xsignal.get() == 3 and Ysignal.get() == 4): # mode CBI/CBV
5681  ylo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
5682  xlo = VBuffB[t] - CHBOffset
5683  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv2 * ylo)
5684  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv2 * xlo)
5685  elif (Xsignal.get() == 4 and Ysignal.get() == 3): # mode CBV/CBI

5687  xlo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
5688  ylo = int(c1 - Yconv2 * ylo)
5689  xlo = int(c2 + XIconv2 * xlo)
5690  elif (Xsignal.get() == 4 and Ysignal.get() == 2): # mode CAI/CBI
5691  ylo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5692  xlo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
5693  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv1 * ylo)
5694  xlo = int(c2 + XIconv2 * xlo)
5695  elif (Xsignal.get() == 2 and Ysignal.get() == 4): # mode CBI/CAI

5697  xlo = (IBuffA[t]) - CHAIOffset
5698  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv2 * ylo)
5699  xlo = int(c2 + XIconv1 * xlo)
5700  elif (Xsignal.get() == 1 and Ysignal.get() == 4): # mode CBI/CAV
5701  ylo = (IBuffB[t]) - CHBIOffset
5702  xlo = VBuffA[t] - CHAOffset
5703  ylo = int(c1 - YIconv2 * ylo)
5704  xlo = int(c2 + Xconv1 * xlo)
5705  elif (Xsignal.get() == 5 and Ysignal.get() == 5): # mode MathYString/MathXString
5706  try:

5710  except:

5716  except:

5718  if ylo < YminXY: # clip waveform if going off grid

5720  if ylo > YmaxXY:

5723  xlo = XminXY
5724  if xlo > XmaxXY:
5725  xlo = XmaxXY
5726  TXYline.append(int(xlo))
5727  TXYline.append(int(ylo))
5728  t = int(t + 1)

6514 def MakeXYScreen():

6533  global CHBIsbxy # spinbox Index for channel 2 I

6540  global TRIGGERsample, TRIGGERlevel, HoldOff, HoldOffentry

6568  #
6569  Ymin = Y0TXY # Minimum position of screen grid (top)
6570  Ymax = Y0TXY + GRHXY # Maximum position of screen grid (bottom)
6571  try:
6572  InOffA = float(eval(CHAVOffsetEntry.get()))
6573  except:
6574  CHAVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)
6575  CHAVOffsetEntry.insert(0, InOffA)
6576  try:
6577  InGainA = float(eval(CHAVGainEntry.get()))
6578  except:
6579  CHAVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
6580  CHAVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainA)

6583  except:
6584  CHBVOffsetEntry.delete(0,END)

6586  try:
6587  InGainB = float(eval(CHBVGainEntry.get()))
6588  except:
6589  CHBVGainEntry.delete(0,END)
6590  CHBVGainEntry.insert(0, InGainB)

6592  try:
6593  CH1pdvRange = float(eval(CHAsbxy.get()))
6594  except:

6599  except:
6600  CHBsbxy.delete(0,END)
6601  CHBsbxy.insert(0, CH2vpdvRange)

6604  except:

6609  except:
6610  CHBIsbxy.delete(0,END)
6611  CHBIsbxy.insert(0, CH2IpdvRange)

6613  try:
6614  CHAOffset = float(eval(CHAVPosEntryxy.get()))
6615  except:
6616  CHAVPosEntryxy.delete(0,END)
6617  CHAVPosEntryxy.insert(0, CHAOffset)
6618  try:

6620  except:

6625  except:

6627  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, CHBOffset)
6628  try:
6629  CHBIOffset = float(eval(CHBIPosEntryxy.get()))
6630  except:
6631  CHBIPosEntryxy.delete(0,END)
6632  CHBIPosEntryxy.insert(0, CHBIOffset)
6633  # prevent divide by zero error
6634  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
6635  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
6636  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
6637  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
6638  if CH1IpdvRange < 0.05:
6639  CH1IpdvRange = 0.05
6640  if CH2IpdvRange < 0.05:
6641  CH2IpdvRange = 0.05
6642  # If drawing histograms adjust offset based on range such that bottom grid is zero
6643  if Xsignal.get() == 6:
6644  CHAIOffset = 5 * CH1IpdvRange
6645  if Xsignal.get() == 7:
6646  CHBIOffset = 5 * CH2IpdvRange
6647  if ScreenXYrefresh.get() == 0:
6648  # Delete all items on the screen
6649  de = XYca.find_enclosed( -1000, -1000, CANVASwidthXY+1000, CANVASheightXY+1000)
6650  MarkerNum = 0
6651  for n in de:
6652  XYca.delete(n)
6653  # Draw horizontal grid lines
6654  i = 0
6655  x1 = X0LXY
6656  x2 = X0LXY + GRWXY
6657  mg_siz = GRWXY/10.0
6658  mg_inc = mg_siz/5.0
6659  while (i < 11):
6660  y = Y0TXY + i * GRHXY/10.0
6661  Dline = [x1,y,x2,y]
6662  if i == 5:
6663  XYca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORzeroline, width=GridWidth.get()) # Blue line at center of grid
6664  k = 0
6665  while (k < 10):
6666  l = 1
6667  while (l < 5):
6668  Dline = [x1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc,y-5,x1+k*mg_siz+l*mg_inc,y+5]
6669  XYca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
6670  l = l + 1
6671  k = k + 1

7289 def onCanvasClickScroll(event):
7290  global ShowTCur, ShowVCur, TCursor, VCursor, RUNstatus, ca
7291  if event.widget == ca:
7292  if ShowTCur.get() > 0 or ShowVCur.get() > 0: # move cursors if shown
7293  ShiftKeyDwn = event.state & 1
7294  if ShowTCur.get() > 0 and ShiftKeyDwn == 0:
7295  TCursor = TCursor + event.delta/100
7296  elif ShowVCur.get() > 0 or ShiftKeyDwn == 1:
7297  VCursor = VCursor - event.delta/100
7298  else:
7299  try:
7300  onSpinBoxScroll(event) # if cursor are not showing scroll the Horx time base
7301  except:
7302  donothing()
7303  if RUNstatus.get() == 0:
7304  UpdateTimeScreen()

7515 def onCanvasClickLeft(event):
7516  global X0L # Left top X value
7517  global Y0T # Left top Y value
7518  global GRW # Screenwidth
7519  global GRH # Screenheight
7520  global FontSize
7521  global ca, MarkerLoc
7522  global HoldOffentry, Xsignal, Ysignal, COLORgrid, COLORtext
7523  global TMsb, CHAsb, CHBsb, CHAIsb, CHBIsb, MarkerScale
7524  global CHAVPosEntry, CHAIPosEntry, CHBVPosEntry, CHBIPosEntry
7525  global SAMPLErate, RUNstatus, MarkerNum, PrevV, PrevT
7526  global COLORtrace1, COLORtrace2, MathUnits, MathXUnits, MathYUnits
7527  global CH1pdvRange, CH2pdvRange, CH1IpdvRange, CH2IpdvRange
7528  global CHAOffset, CHAIOffset, CHBOffset, CHBIOffset
7529  global CHB_Asb, CHB_APosEntry, CHB_Bsb, CHB_BPosEntry
7530  global CHB_Csb, CHB_CPosEntry, CHB_Dsb, CHB_DPosEntry
7531  global MeasGateLeft, MeasGateRight, MeasGateStatus, MeasGateNum, TMsb, SAMPLErate
7532 
7533  try:
7534  HoldOff = float(eval(HoldOffentry.get()))
7535  if HoldOff < 0:
7536  HoldOff = 0
7537  except:
7538  HoldOffentry.delete(0,END)
7539  HoldOffentry.insert(0, HoldOff)
7540  # get time scale
7541  try:
7542  TIMEdiv = float(eval(TMsb.get()))
7543  except:
7544  TIMEdiv = 0.5
7545  TMsb.delete(0,"end")
7546  TMsb.insert(0,TIMEdiv)
7547  # prevent divide by zero error
7548  if TIMEdiv < 0.0002:
7549  TIMEdiv = 0.01
7550  # add markers only if stopped
7551  if (RUNstatus.get() == 0):
7552  MarkerNum = MarkerNum + 1
7553  # get the vertical ranges
7554  try:
7555  CH1pdvRange = float(eval(CHAsb.get()))
7556  except:
7557  CHAsb.delete(0,END)
7558  CHAsb.insert(0, CH1vpdvRange)
7559  try:
7560  CH2pdvRange = float(eval(CHBsb.get()))
7561  except:
7562  CHBsb.delete(0,END)
7563  CHBsb.insert(0, CH2vpdvRange)
7564  try:
7565  CH1IpdvRange = float(eval(CHAIsb.get()))
7566  except:
7567  CHAIsb.delete(0,END)
7568  CHAIsb.insert(0, CH1IpdvRange)
7569  try:
7570  CH2IpdvRange = float(eval(CHBIsb.get()))
7571  except:
7572  CHBIsb.delete(0,END)
7573  CHBIsb.insert(0, CH2IpdvRange)
7574  # get the vertical offsets
7575  try:
7576  CHAOffset = float(eval(CHAVPosEntry.get()))
7577  except:
7578  CHAVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
7579  CHAVPosEntry.insert(0, CHAOffset)
7580  try:
7581  CHAIOffset = float(eval(CHAIPosEntry.get()))
7582  except:
7583  CHAIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
7584  CHAIPosEntry.insert(0, CHAIOffset)
7585  try:
7586  CHBOffset = float(eval(CHBVPosEntry.get()))
7587  except:
7588  CHBVPosEntry.delete(0,END)
7589  CHBVPosEntry.insert(0, CHBOffset)
7590  try:
7591  CHBIOffset = float(eval(CHBIPosEntry.get()))
7592  except:
7593  CHBIPosEntry.delete(0,END)
7594  CHBIPosEntry.insert(0, CHBIOffset)
7595  # prevent divide by zero error
7596  if CH1pdvRange < 0.001:
7597  CH1pdvRange = 0.001
7598  if CH2pdvRange < 0.001:
7599  CH2pdvRange = 0.001
7600  if CH1IpdvRange < 1.0:
7601  CH1IpdvRange = 1.0
7602  if CH2IpdvRange < 1.0:
7603  CH2IpdvRange = 1.0
7604 #
7605  if MuxScreenStatus.get() == 1: # if using analog Mux set up axis controls
7606  try:
7607  CHMApdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Asb.get()))
7608  except:
7609  CHB_Asb.delete(0,END)
7610  CHB_Asb.insert(0, CHMApdvRange)
7611  try:
7612  CHMBpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Bsb.get()))
7613  except:
7614  CHB_Bsb.delete(0,END)
7615  CHB_Bsb.insert(0, CHMBpdvRange)
7616  try:
7617  CHMCpdvRange = float(eval(CHB_Csb.get()))
7618  except:
7619  CHB_Csb.delete(0,END)
7620  CHB_Csb.insert(0, CHMCpdvRange)
7621  try:

8004 def Wrap(InArray, WrFactor):
8005  # Build new array by skipping WrFactor samples and wrapping back around
8006  # [1,2,3,4,5,6} becomes [1,3,5,2,4,6]
8007  # effectively multiplies the frequency content by WrFactor
8008  OutArray = []
8009  OutArray = numpy.array(OutArray)
8010  InArray = numpy.array(InArray)
8011  EndIndex = len(InArray)
8012  StartIndex = 0
8013  while StartIndex < WrFactor:
8014  OutArray = numpy.concatenate((OutArray, InArray[StartIndex:EndIndex:WrFactor]), axis=0)
8015  StartIndex = StartIndex + 1
8016  return OutArray
8017 #
8018 def UnWrap(InArray, WrFactor):
8019  # Build new array by splitting arrray into WrFactor sections and interleaving samples from each section
8020  # [1,2,3,4,5,6} becomes [1,4,2,5,3,6]
8021  # effectively divided the frequency content by WrFactor
8022  OutArray = []
8023  InArray = numpy.array(InArray)
8024  EndIndex = int(len(InArray)/WrFactor)
8025  StartIndex = 0
8026  while StartIndex < EndIndex:
8027  LoopIndex = 0
8028  while LoopIndex < WrFactor:
8029  OutArray.append(InArray[StartIndex+LoopIndex])
8030  LoopIndex = LoopIndex + 1
8031  StartIndex = StartIndex + 1
8032  OutArray = numpy.array(OutArray)
8033  return OutArray
8034 #
8035 def Write_WAV(data, repeat, filename):
8036  global SAMPLErate
8037  # write data array to mono .wav file 100KSPS
8038  # copy buffer repeat times in output file
8039  # Use : Write_WAV(VBuffB, 2, "write_wave_1.wav")
8040  wavfile = wave.open(filename, "w")
8041  nchannels = 1
8042  sampwidth = 2
8043  framerate = SAMPLErate
8044  amplitude = 32766
8045  nframes = len(data)
8046  comptype = "NONE"
8047  compname = "not compressed"
8048  wavfile.setparams((nchannels,
8049  sampwidth,
8050  framerate,
8051  nframes,
8052  comptype,
8053  compname))
8054  # Normalize data
8055  ArrN = numpy.array(data)
8056  ArrN /= numpy.max(numpy.abs(data))
8057  frames = []
8058  for s in ArrN:
8059  mul = int(s * amplitude)
8060  # print "s: %f mul: %d" % (s, mul)
8061  frames.append(struct.pack('h', mul))
8062  print len(frames)
8063  frames = ''.join(frames)
8064  print len(frames)
8065  for x in xrange(0, repeat):
8066  print x
8067  wavfile.writeframes(frames)
8068  wavfile.close()

8071 def BAWGAAmpl(temp):
8072  global AWGAAmplEntry, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAMode, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8073 
8074  try:
8075  AWGAAmplvalue = float(eval(AWGAAmplEntry.get()))
8076  except:
8077  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8078  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8079  #
8080  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max mode
8081  if AWGAMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
8082  if AWGAAmplvalue > 5.00:
8083  AWGAAmplvalue = 5.00
8084  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8085  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8086  if AWGAAmplvalue < 0.00:
8087  AWGAAmplvalue = 0.00
8088  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8089  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8090  elif AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1: # 1 = Amp/Offset
8091  if AWGAMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
8092  if AWGAAmplvalue > 2.5:
8093  AWGAAmplvalue = 2.5
8094  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8095  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8096  if AWGAAmplvalue < -2.50:
8097  AWGAAmplvalue = -2.50
8098  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8099  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8100  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
8101  if AWGAAmplvalue > 200.00:
8102  AWGAAmplvalue = 200.00
8103  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8104  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)
8105  if AWGAAmplvalue < -200.00:
8106  AWGAAmplvalue = -200.00
8107  AWGAAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
8108  AWGAAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGAAmplvalue)

8149  AWGAFreqvalue = 90000

8151  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0, AWGAFreqvalue)
8152  else:
8153  if AWGAFreqvalue > 50000: # max freq is 50KHz
8154  AWGAFreqvalue = 50000
8155  AWGAFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
8156  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0, AWGAFreqvalue)
8157  else:
8158  if AWGAFreqvalue > 25000: # max freq is 25KHz
8159  AWGAFreqvalue = 25000
8160  AWGAFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
8161  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0, AWGAFreqvalue)
8162  if AWGAFreqvalue < 0: # Set negative frequency entry to 0
8163  AWGAFreqvalue = 10
8164  AWGAFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
8165  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0, AWGAFreqvalue)

8313 def AWGAReadWAV():
8314  global AWGAwaveform, AWGALength, AWGAShape, awgwindow, AWGBwaveform, AWGBLength, AWGBShape
8315  global AWG_2X, AWGA2X
8316 
8317 # Read values from WAV file
8318  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".wav", filetypes=[("WAV files", "*.wav")], parent=awgwindow)
8319  try:
8320  spf = wave.open(filename,'r')
8321  except:
8322  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent=awgwindow)
8323  AWGAwaveform = []
8324  AWGBwaveform = []
8325  Length = spf.getnframes()
8326  if Length > 90000:
8327  Length = 90000
8328  # If Stereo put first channel in AWGA and second channel in AWGB
8329  if spf.getnchannels() == 2:
8330  showwarning("Split Stereo","Left to AWGA Right to AWGB", parent=awgwindow)
8331  signal = spf.readframes(Length)
8332  Stereo = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int
8333  n = 0
8334  while n < Length*2:
8335  AWGAwaveform.append((Stereo[n] * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5)
8336  n = n + 1
8337  AWGBwaveform.append((Stereo[n] * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5)
8338  n = n + 1
8339  AWGAwaveform = numpy.array(AWGAwaveform)
8340  AWGBwaveform = numpy.array(AWGBwaveform)
8341  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(len(AWGAwaveform))) # change displayed value
8342  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(len(AWGBwaveform))) # change displayed value
8343  AWGBShape.set(AWGAShape.get())
8344  else:
8345  #Extract Raw Audio from Wav File
8346  signal = spf.readframes(Length)
8347  WAVsignal = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int
8348  # offset and scale for 0 5 V range
8349  AWGAwaveform = (WAVsignal * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5
8350  AWGAwaveform = numpy.array(AWGAwaveform)
8351  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8352  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(len(AWGAwaveform))) # change displayed value
8353  spf.close()
8354  UpdateAwgCont()

8380 def AWGAMakeBodeSine():
8381  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
8382  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWGAMode
8383  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, phasealab
8384 
8385  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8386  BAWGAOffset(0)
8387  BAWGAFreq(0)
8388  BAWGAPhase(0)
8389  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8390 
8391  if AWGAFreqvalue < 10.0: # if frequency is less than 10 Hz use libsmu sine function
8392  AWGAShape.set(1)
8393  BAWGAShape()
8394  UpdateAwgCont()
8395  return
8396 
8397  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8398  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8399  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
8400  else:
8401  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8402  else:
8403  AWGAperiodvalue = 10.0
8404 
8405  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
8406  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
8407  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
8408  else:
8409  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
8410  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
8411  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
8412  Cycles = int(32768/AWGAperiodvalue)
8413  if Cycles < 1:
8414  Cycles = 1
8415  RecLength = int(Cycles * AWGAperiodvalue)
8416  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8417  RecLength = RecLength + 1
8418  AWGAwaveform = []
8419  AWGAwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*Cycles*numpy.pi, RecLength))
8420  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
8421  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
8422  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
8423  else:
8424  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2.0
8425  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2.0
8426  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
8427  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
8428 #
8429  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8430  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8431  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
8432  duty1lab.config(text="%")
8433  phasealab.config(text="Delay")
8434  UpdateAwgCont()
