8436 def AWGAMakeFMSine():
8437  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
8438  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWGAMode
8439  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, phasealab
8440 
8441  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8442  BAWGAOffset(0)
8443  BAWGAFreq(0)
8444 # uses dyty cycle entry for Modulation index and phase entry for Modulation frequency
8445  duty1lab.config(text = "M Index")
8446  phasealab.config(text = "M Freq")
8447 
8448  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8449  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8450  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
8451  else:
8452  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8453  else:
8454  AWGAperiodvalue = 10.0
8455 
8456  try:
8457  ModFreq = float(eval(AWGAPhaseEntry.get()))
8458  except:
8459  ModFreq = 10
8460  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
8461  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
8462 
8463  if ModFreq < 10:
8464  ModFreq = 10
8465  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
8466  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
8467 
8468  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8469  MODperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/ModFreq
8470  else:
8471  MODperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/ModFreq
8472 
8473  try:
8474  ModIndex = float(eval(AWGADutyCycleEntry.get()))
8475  except:
8476  ModIndex = 1.0
8477  AWGADutyCycleEntry.delete(0,"end")
8478  AWGADutyCycleEntry.insert(0, ModIndex)
8479 
8480  ModCycles = int(32768/MODperiodvalue) # find a whole number of cycles
8481  if ModCycles < 1:
8482  ModCycles = 1
8483  RecLength = int(ModCycles * MODperiodvalue)
8484  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8485  RecLength = RecLength + 1
8486  CarCycles = int(RecLength/AWGAperiodvalue) # insure a whole number of carrier cycles in record
8487  AWGAwaveform = []
8488  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sin( (numpy.linspace(0, CarCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) - ModIndex*numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, ModCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) )
8489  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
8490  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
8491  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
8492  else:
8493  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2.0
8494  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2.0
8495  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
8496  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
8497 #
8498  SplitAWGAwaveform() # if needed
8499  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8500  UpdateAwgCont()

8502 def AWGAMakeAMSine():
8503  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
8504  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWGAMode
8505  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, phasealab
8506 
8507  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8508  BAWGAOffset(0)
8509  BAWGAFreq(0)
8510 # uses dyty cycle entry for Modulation index and phase entry for Modulation frequency
8511  duty1lab.config(text = "M Index")
8512  phasealab.config(text = "M Freq")
8513 
8514  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8515  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8516  AWGAperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue
8517  else:
8518  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8519  else:
8520  AWGAperiodvalue = 10.0
8521 
8522  try:
8523  ModFreq = float(eval(AWGAPhaseEntry.get()))
8524  except:
8525  ModFreq = 10
8526  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
8527  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
8528 
8529  if ModFreq < 10:
8530  ModFreq = 10
8531  AWGAPhaseEntry.delete(0,"end")
8532  AWGAPhaseEntry.insert(0, ModFreq)
8533 
8534  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8535  MODperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/ModFreq
8536  else:
8537  MODperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/ModFreq
8538 
8539  try:
8540  ModIndex = float(eval(AWGADutyCycleEntry.get()))/200.0
8541  except:
8542  ModIndex = 50.0
8543  AWGADutyCycleEntry.delete(0,"end")
8544  AWGADutyCycleEntry.insert(0, ModIndex)
8545 
8546  ModCycles = int(32768/MODperiodvalue) # find a whole number of cycles
8547  if ModCycles < 1:
8548  ModCycles = 1
8549  RecLength = int(ModCycles * MODperiodvalue)
8550  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8551  RecLength = RecLength + 1
8552  CarCycles = int(RecLength/AWGAperiodvalue) # insure a whole number of carrier cycles in record
8553  AWGAwaveform = []
8554  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sin(numpy.linspace(0, CarCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)) * (0.5+(ModIndex*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, ModCycles*2*numpy.pi, RecLength)))))
8555  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
8556  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2000.0
8557  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2000.0
8558  else:
8559  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue) / -2.0
8560  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue) / 2.0
8561  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
8562  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
8563 #
8564  SplitAWGAwaveform() # if needed
8565  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8566  UpdateAwgCont()

8568 def AWGAMakePWMSine():
8569  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength
8570  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8571  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
8572 
8573  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8574  BAWGAOffset(0)
8575  BAWGAFreq(0)
8576  BAWGAPhase(0)
8577  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8578 
8579  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8580  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8581  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
8582  else:
8583  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8584  else:
8585  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
8586  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
8587  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
8588  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
8589  else:
8590  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
8591  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
8592 
8593  PulseWidth = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
8594  PulseSamples = int(AWGAperiodvalue/PulseWidth)
8595  AWGAwaveform = []
8596  for i in range(PulseSamples): #(i = 0; i < cPulse; i++)
8597  v = round(PulseWidth/2*(1+numpy.sin(i*2*numpy.pi/PulseSamples)))
8598  # print(v)
8599  for j in range(PulseWidth): #(j = 0; j < cLength; j++)
8600  if j >= v:
8601  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV) # j>=v?1:0
8602  else:
8603  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV) # j>=v?1:0
8604  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8605  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8606  duty1lab.config(text="PWidth")
8607  UpdateAwgCont()
8608 #
8609 def AWGAMakeFourier():
8610  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength
8611  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8612  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
8613 
8614  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8615  BAWGAOffset(0)
8616  BAWGAFreq(0)
8617  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8618 
8619  Max_term = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
8620  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8621  TempRate = (BaseSampleRate*2)
8622  else:
8623  TempRate = BaseSampleRate
8624  AWGAwaveform = []
8625  AWGAwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGAFreqvalue)) # the fundamental
8626  k = 3
8627  while k <= Max_term:
8628  # Add odd harmonics up to max_term
8629  Harmonic = (math.sin(k*numpy.pi/2.0)/k)*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, k*2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGAFreqvalue)))
8630  AWGAwaveform = AWGAwaveform + Harmonic
8631  k = k + 2 # skip even numbers
8632  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
8633  amplitude = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)/2.0
8634  offset = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)/2.0
8635  else:
8636  amplitude = AWGAAmplvalue
8637  offset = AWGAOffsetvalue
8638  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
8639  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8640  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8641  duty1lab.config(text="Harmonics")
8642  UpdateAwgCont()

8644 def AWGAMakeSinc():
8645  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSampleRate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue
8646  global AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAFreqvalue, duty1lab, AWGAgain, AWGAoffset, AWGAPhaseDelay
8647  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8648 
8649  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8650  BAWGAOffset(0)
8651  BAWGAFreq(0)
8652  BAWGAPhase(0)
8653  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8654 
8655  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8656  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8657  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
8658  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
8659  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8660  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
8661  else:
8662  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8663  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
8664  else:
8665  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
8666  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
8667  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
8668  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
8669  else:
8670  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
8671  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
8672 
8673  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
8674  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
8675  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
8676  else:
8677  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
8678  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
8679  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
8680 
8681  Cycles = int(AWGADutyCyclevalue*100)
8682  NCycles = -1 * Cycles
8683  AWGAwaveform = []
8684  AWGAwaveform = numpy.sinc(numpy.linspace(NCycles, Cycles, SAMPLErate/AWGAFreqvalue))
8685  amplitude = (MaxV-MinV) / 2.0
8686  offset = (MaxV+MinV) / 2.0
8687  AWGAwaveform = (AWGAwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
8688  Cycles = int(37500/AWGAperiodvalue)
8689  if Cycles < 1:
8690  Cycles = 1
8691  if Cycles > 1:
8692  Extend = int((Cycles-1.0)*AWGAperiodvalue/2.0)
8693  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (Extend,Extend), 'wrap')
8694  AWGAwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGAwaveform, int(AWGAdelayvalue))
8695  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8696  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8697  #BAWGAPhaseDelay()
8698  duty1lab.config(text="Cycles")
8699  UpdateAwgCont()

8701 def AWGAMakeSSQ():
8702  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, phasealab, duty1lab
8703  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8704  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
8705  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
8706 
8707  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8708  BAWGAOffset(0)
8709  BAWGAFreq(0)
8710  BAWGAPhase(0)
8711  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8712 
8713  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8714  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8715  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
8716  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
8717  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8718  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
8719  else:
8720  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
8721  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
8722  else:
8723  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
8724  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
8725  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
8726  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
8727  else:
8728  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
8729  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
8730  AWGAwaveform = []
8731  SlopeValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
8732  if SlopeValue <= 0:
8733  SlopeValue = 1
8734  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue)
8735  if PulseWidth <=0:
8736  PulseWidth = 1
8737  Remainder = int((AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth - SlopeValue)/2)
8738  if Remainder <= 0:
8739  Remainder = 1
8740  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
8741  if PulseWidth <=0:
8742  PulseWidth = 1
8743  StepAmp = (MaxV - MinV)/2
8744  StepOff = (MaxV + MinV)/2
8745  AWGAwaveform = StepAmp * (numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, SlopeValue*2))) + StepOff
8746  MidArray = numpy.ones(PulseWidth) * MinV
8747  AWGAwaveform = numpy.insert(AWGAwaveform, SlopeValue, MidArray)
8748  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (Remainder, Remainder), 'edge')
8749  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
8750  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
8751  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
8752  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
8753  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS/2) # convert mS to samples
8754  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, TempDelay), 'edge')
8755  SplitAWGAwaveform()
8756  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
8757  duty1lab.config(text="%")
8758  phasealab.config(text = "Rise Time")
8759  UpdateAwgCont()

8961 def AWGAMakeUpDownRamp():
8962  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, duty1lab
8963  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
8964  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
8965  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
8966 
8967  BAWGAAmpl(0)
8968  BAWGAOffset(0)
8969  BAWGAFreq(0)
8970  BAWGAPhase(0)
8971  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
8972 
8973  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
8974  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
8975  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
8976  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
8977  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
8978  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
8979  else:
8980  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGSAMPLErate/AWGAFreqvalue
8981  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
8982  else:
8983  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
8984  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
8985  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
8986  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
8987  else:
8988  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
8989  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
8990  #
8991  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
8992  if AWGAPhasevalue > 0:
8993  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAperiodvalue * AWGAPhasevalue / 360.0
8994  else:
8995  AWGAdelayvalue = 0.0
8996  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
8997  AWGAdelayvalue = AWGAPhasevalue * SAMPLErate / 1000
8998  #
8999  AWGAwaveform = []
9000  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue)
9001  if PulseWidth <=0:
9002  PulseWidth = 1
9003  Remainder = int(AWGAperiodvalue - PulseWidth)
9004  if Remainder <= 0:
9005  Remainder = 1
9006  UpStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / PulseWidth
9007  DownStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / Remainder
9008  SampleValue = MinV
9009  for i in range(PulseWidth):
9010  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
9011  SampleValue = SampleValue + UpStepValue
9012  for i in range(Remainder):
9013  AWGAwaveform.append(SampleValue)
9014  SampleValue = SampleValue - DownStepValue

9016  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
9017  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
9018  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
9019  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
9020  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
9021  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
9022  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9023  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9024  BAWGAPhaseDelay()
9025  duty1lab.config(text = "Symmetry")
9026  UpdateAwgCont()

9028 def AWGAMakeImpulse():
9029  global AWGAwaveform, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGALength, AWGAPhaseDelay, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
9030  global AWGAFreqvalue, AWGAperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGADutyCyclevalue, AWGAPhasevalue
9031  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
9032  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9033 
9034  BAWGAAmpl(0)
9035  BAWGAOffset(0)
9036  BAWGAFreq(0)
9037  BAWGAPhase(0)
9038  BAWGADutyCycle(0)
9039 
9040  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
9041  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9042  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
9043  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
9044  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9045  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
9046  else:
9047  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
9048  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
9049  else:
9050  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
9051  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
9052  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
9053  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
9054  else:
9055  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
9056  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
9057  AWGAwaveform = []
9058  PulseWidth = int(AWGAperiodvalue * AWGADutyCyclevalue / 2.0)
9059  if AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
9060  DelayValue = int(AWGAperiodvalue*(AWGAPhasevalue/360))
9061  elif AWGAPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
9062  DelayValue = int(AWGAPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
9063  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
9064  AWGAwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2.0)
9065  for i in range(PulseWidth):
9066  AWGAwaveform.append(MaxV)
9067  for i in range(PulseWidth):
9068  AWGAwaveform.append(MinV)
9069  DelayValue = int(AWGAperiodvalue-DelayValue)
9070  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
9071  AWGAwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2.0)
9072  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
9073  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
9074  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
9075  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
9076  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
9077  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
9078  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9079  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9080  UpdateAwgCont()

9082 def AWGAMakeUUNoise():
9083  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGAFreqvalue
9084  global AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
9085  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
9086  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9087 
9088  BAWGAAmpl(0)
9089  BAWGAOffset(0)
9090  BAWGAFreq(0)
9091 
9092  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
9093  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9094  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
9095  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
9096  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9097  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
9098  else:
9099  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
9100  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
9101  else:
9102  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
9103  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
9104  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
9105  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
9106  else:
9107  if AWGAAmplvalue > AWGAOffsetvalue:
9108  MinV = AWGAOffsetvalue
9109  MaxV = AWGAAmplvalue
9110  else:
9111  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
9112  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
9113  AWGAwaveform = []
9114  AWGAwaveform = numpy.random.uniform(MinV, MaxV, int(AWGAperiodvalue))
9115  Mid = (MaxV+MinV)/2.0
9116  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
9117  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
9118  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
9119  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
9120  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
9121  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'constant', constant_values=(Mid))
9122  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9123  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9124  UpdateAwgCont()

9126 def AWGAMakeUGNoise():
9127  global AWGAwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGAAmplvalue, AWGAOffsetvalue, AWGAFreqvalue
9128  global AWGALength, AWGAperiodvalue, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
9129  global AWGABurstFlag, AWGACycles, AWGABurstDelay
9130  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9131 
9132  BAWGAAmpl(0)
9133  BAWGAOffset(0)
9134  BAWGAFreq(0)
9135 
9136  if AWGAFreqvalue > 0.0:
9137  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9138  AWGAperiodvalue = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGAFreqvalue)
9139  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
9140  if AWGAperiodvalue % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9141  AWGAperiodvalue = AWGAperiodvalue + 1
9142  else:
9143  AWGAperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGAFreqvalue
9144  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
9145  else:
9146  AWGAperiodvalue = 0.0
9147  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
9148  MaxV = (AWGAOffsetvalue+AWGAAmplvalue)
9149  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)
9150  else:
9151  if AWGAAmplvalue > AWGAOffsetvalue:
9152  MinV = AWGAOffsetvalue
9153  MaxV = AWGAAmplvalue
9154  else:
9155  MaxV = AWGAOffsetvalue
9156  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
9157  AWGAwaveform = []
9158  AWGAwaveform = numpy.random.normal((MinV+MaxV)/2, (MaxV-MinV)/3, int(AWGAperiodvalue))
9159  Mid = (MaxV+MinV)/2.0
9160  if AWGABurstFlag.get() == 1:
9161  TempOneCycle = AWGAwaveform
9162  for i in range(AWGACycles-1):
9163  AWGAwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGAwaveform, TempOneCycle))
9164  TempDelay = int(AWGABurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
9165  AWGAwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGAwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'constant', constant_values=(Mid))
9166  SplitAWGAwaveform()
9167  AWGALength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGAwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9168  UpdateAwgCont()

9182  if AWGAMode.get() == 0:

9234  elif AWGATerm.get() == 1: # 50 Ohm termination to GND
9235  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
9236  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to closed
9237  elif AWGATerm.get() == 2: # 50 Ohm termination to +2.5 Volts
9238  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 32, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to closed
9239  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 33, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
9240 
9241  if AWGAWave == 'dc':
9242  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
9243  AWGAWave == 'arbitrary'
9244  CHA.arbitrary(AWGB2X, AWGBRepeatFlag.get())
9245  else:

9249  else:

9251  CHA.constant(AWGAOffsetvalue)
9252  #
9253  if AWGAMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
9254  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:

9256  else:

9259  #
9260  if AWGAMode.get() == 2: # High impedance mode

9263  else:
9264  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode

9284  if AWGAMode.get() == 2: # High impedance mode
9285  if AWGAIOMode.get() == 0:
9286  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHA in Hi Z mode
9287  else:
9288  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode
9289  else:

9292  MinV = (AWGAOffsetvalue-AWGAAmplvalue)

9295  MinV = AWGAAmplvalue
9296  try:

9299  elif AWGAWave == 'triangle':

9311  AWGAWave == 'arbitrary'

9313  else:
9314  CHA.arbitrary(AWGAwaveform, AWGARepeatFlag.get()) # set repeat flag
9315  except:
9316  donothing()
9317  if AWGAIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
9318  if HWRevOne == "D":
9319  AWGAMode.set(1)
9320  CHA.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode

9364 def BAWGBAmpl(temp):

9366 
9367  try:
9368  AWGBAmplvalue = float(eval(AWGBAmplEntry.get()))
9369  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
9370  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max
9371  if AWGBAmplvalue > 5.00:
9372  AWGBAmplvalue = 5.00
9373  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9374  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9375  if AWGBAmplvalue < 0.00:
9376  AWGBAmplvalue = 0.00
9377  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9378  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9379  elif AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1: # 1 = Amp/Offset
9380  if AWGBAmplvalue > 2.5:
9381  AWGBAmplvalue = 2.5
9382  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9383  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9384  if AWGBAmplvalue < -2.50:
9385  AWGBAmplvalue = -2.50
9386  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9387  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9388  elif AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure voltage mode
9389  if AWGBAmplvalue > 200.00:
9390  AWGBAmplvalue = 200.00
9391  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9392  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9393  if AWGBAmplvalue < -200.00:
9394  AWGBAmplvalue = -200.00
9395  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9396  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)
9397  except:
9398  AWGBAmplEntry.delete(0,"end")
9399  AWGBAmplEntry.insert(0, AWGBAmplvalue)

9591 def AWGBReadWAV():
9592  global AWGBwaveform, AWGBLength, awgwindow
9593  global AWG_2X, AWGA2X
9594 
9595 # Read values from WAV file
9596  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".wav", filetypes=[("WAV files", "*.wav")], parent=awgwindow)
9597  try:
9598  spf = wave.open(filename,'r')
9599  except:
9600  showwarning("WARNING","No such file found or wrong format!", parent=awgwindow)
9601  AWGBwaveform = []
9602  #If Stereo
9603  if spf.getnchannels() == 2:
9604  showwarning("WARNING","Only mono files supported!", parent=awgwindow)
9605  return()
9606  #Extract Raw Audio from Wav File
9607  Length = spf.getnframes()
9608  if Length > 90000: # limit to first 90K samples
9609  Length = 90000
9610  signal = spf.readframes(Length)
9611  WAVsignal = numpy.fromstring(signal, 'Int16') # convert strings to Int
9612  # offset and scale for 0 5 V range
9613  AWGBwaveform = (WAVsignal * 2.5 / 32768) + 2.5
9614  AWGBwaveform = numpy.array(AWGBwaveform)
9615  SplitAWGBwaveform()
9616  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(len(AWGBwaveform))) # change displayed value
9617  spf.close()
9618  UpdateAwgCont()

9644 def AWGBMakeFourier():
9645  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBFreqvalue, awgwindow
9646  global AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
9647  global AWGA2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9648 
9649  Max_termStr = askstring("AWG B Fourier", "\nEnter Max Harmonic:\n", parent=awgwindow)
9650  if (Max_termStr == None): # If Cancel pressed, then None
9651  return
9652  Max_term = int(Max_termStr)
9653 
9654  BAWGBAmpl(0)
9655  BAWGBOffset(0)
9656  BAWGBFreq(0)
9657  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
9658  TempRate = (BaseSampleRate*2)
9659  else:
9660  TempRate = BaseSampleRate
9661  AWGBwaveform = []
9662  AWGBwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGBFreqvalue)) # the fundamental
9663  k = 3
9664  while k <= Max_term:
9665  # Add odd harmonics up to max_term
9666  Harmonic = (math.sin(k*numpy.pi/2)/k)*(numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, k*2*numpy.pi, TempRate/AWGBFreqvalue)))
9667  AWGBwaveform = AWGBwaveform + Harmonic
9668  k = k + 2 # skip even numbers
9669  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0:
9670  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)/2
9671  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)/2
9672  else:
9673  amplitude = AWGBAmplvalue
9674  offset = AWGBOffsetvalue
9675  AWGBwaveform = (AWGBwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
9676  SplitAWGBwaveform()
9677  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGBwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9678  duty2lab.config(text="Harmonics")
9679  UpdateAwgCont()

9681 def AWGBMakeBodeSine():
9682  global AWGBwaveform, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBperiodvalue
9683  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBFreqvalue, duty2lab, AWGBgain, AWGBoffset, AWGBPhaseDelay, AWGBMode
9684  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9685 
9686  BAWGBAmpl(0)
9687  BAWGBOffset(0)
9688  BAWGBFreq(0)
9689  BAWGBPhase(0)
9690  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
9691 
9692  if AWGBFreqvalue < 10.0: # if frequency is less than 10 Hz use libsmu sine function
9693  AWGBShape.set(1)
9694  BAWGBShape()
9695  UpdateAwgCont()
9696  return
9697 
9698  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
9699  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
9700  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
9701  else:
9702  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
9703  else:
9704  AWGBperiodvalue = 10.0
9705 
9706  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
9707  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
9708  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
9709  else:
9710  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
9711  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
9712  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * AWGSAMPLErate / 1000
9713  Cycles = int(32768/AWGBperiodvalue)
9714  if Cycles < 1:
9715  Cycles = 1
9716  RecLength = int(Cycles * AWGBperiodvalue)
9717  if RecLength % 2 != 0: # make sure record length is even so 2X mode works for all Freq
9718  RecLength = RecLength + 1
9719  AWGBwaveform = []
9720  AWGBwaveform = numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*Cycles*numpy.pi, RecLength))
9721  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # convert to mA
9722  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue) / -2000.0
9723  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue) / 2000.0
9724  else:
9725  amplitude = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue) / -2.0
9726  offset = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue) / 2.0
9727  AWGBwaveform = (AWGBwaveform * amplitude) + offset # scale and offset the waveform
9728  AWGBwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGBwaveform, int(AWGBdelayvalue))
9729  #
9730  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
9731  Tempwaveform = []
9732  AWGB2X = []
9733  AWGB2X = AWGBwaveform[::2] # even numbered samples
9734  Tempwaveform = AWGBwaveform[1::2] # odd numbered samples Tempwaveform
9735  AWGBwaveform = Tempwaveform
9736  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGBwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9737  BAWGBPhaseDelay()
9738  duty2lab.config(text="%")
9739  UpdateAwgCont()

9745 
9746  BAWGBAmpl(0)
9747  BAWGBOffset(0)
9748  BAWGBFreq(0)
9749  BAWGBPhase(0)
9750  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
9751 
9752  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
9753  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
9754  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
9755  else:
9756  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
9757  else:
9758  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0

9764  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue

9775  else:
9776  AWGBwaveform.append(MinV) # j>=v?1:0

9798  else:

9837 def AWGBMakeSSQ():
9838  global AWGBwaveform, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBPhaseDelay
9839  global AWGBFreqvalue, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBPhasevalue
9840  global AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
9841  global AWGBBurstFlag, AWGBCycles, AWGBBurstDelay
9842  global AWGB2X, AWG_2X, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
9843 
9844  BAWGBAmpl(0)
9845  BAWGBOffset(0)
9846  BAWGBFreq(0)
9847  BAWGBPhase(0)
9848  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
9849 
9850  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
9851  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
9852  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
9853  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
9854  else:
9855  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
9856  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
9857  else:
9858  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
9859  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
9860  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)
9861  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)
9862  else:
9863  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
9864  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
9865  AWGBwaveform = []
9866  SlopeValue = int(AWGBPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
9867  if SlopeValue <= 0:
9868  SlopeValue = 1
9869  PulseWidth = int(AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBDutyCyclevalue)
9870  if PulseWidth <=0:
9871  PulseWidth = 1
9872  Remainder = int((AWGBperiodvalue - PulseWidth - SlopeValue)/2)
9873  if Remainder <= 0:
9874  Remainder = 1
9875  PulseWidth = PulseWidth - SlopeValue
9876  if PulseWidth <=0:
9877  PulseWidth = 1
9878  StepAmp = (MaxV - MinV)/2
9879  StepOff = (MaxV + MinV)/2
9880  AWGBwaveform = StepAmp * (numpy.cos(numpy.linspace(0, 2*numpy.pi, SlopeValue*2))) + StepOff
9881  MidArray = numpy.ones(PulseWidth) * MinV
9882  AWGBwaveform = numpy.insert(AWGBwaveform, SlopeValue, MidArray)
9883  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (Remainder, Remainder), 'edge')
9884  if AWGBBurstFlag.get() == 1:
9885  TempOneCycle = AWGBwaveform
9886  for i in range(AWGBCycles-1):
9887  AWGBwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGBwaveform, TempOneCycle))
9888  TempDelay = int(AWGBBurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
9889  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
9890  SplitAWGBwaveform()
9891  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGBwaveform)))) # change displayed value
9892  duty2lab.config(text="%")
9893  phaseblab.config(text = "Rise Time")
9894  UpdateAwgCont()

10100  BAWGBAmpl(0)
10101  BAWGBOffset(0)
10102  BAWGBFreq(0)
10103  BAWGBPhase(0)
10104  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
10105 
10106  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
10107  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
10108  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
10109  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10110  else:
10111  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
10112  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10113  else:
10114  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
10115  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10116  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)
10117  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)
10118  else:
10119  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
10120  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
10121  #
10122  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10123  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
10124  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
10125  else:
10126  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
10127  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10128  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * AWGSAMPLErate / 1000
10129  #
10130  AWGBwaveform = []
10131  PulseWidth = int(AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBDutyCyclevalue)
10132  if PulseWidth <=0:
10133  PulseWidth = 1
10134  Remainder = int(AWGBperiodvalue - PulseWidth)
10135  if Remainder <= 0:
10136  Remainder = 1
10137  UpStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / PulseWidth
10138  DownStepValue = (MaxV - MinV) / Remainder
10139  SampleValue = MinV
10140  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10141  AWGBwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10142  SampleValue = SampleValue + UpStepValue
10143  for i in range(Remainder):
10144  AWGBwaveform.append(SampleValue)
10145  SampleValue = SampleValue - DownStepValue
10146  AWGBwaveform = numpy.roll(AWGBwaveform, int(AWGBdelayvalue))
10147  if AWGBBurstFlag.get() == 1:
10148  TempOneCycle = AWGBwaveform
10149  for i in range(AWGBCycles-1):
10150  AWGBwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGBwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10151  TempDelay = int(AWGBBurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10152  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
10153  SplitAWGBwaveform()
10154  AWGBLength.config(text = "L = " + str(int(len(AWGBwaveform)))) # change displayed value
10155  BAWGBPhaseDelay()
10156  duty2lab.config(text = "Symmetry")
10157  UpdateAwgCont()

10159 def AWGBMakeImpulse():
10160  global AWGBwaveform, AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGBLength, AWGBPhaseDelay
10161  global AWGBFreqvalue, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGSAMPLErate, AWGBDutyCyclevalue, AWGBPhasevalue
10162  global AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10163  global AWGBBurstFlag, AWGBCycles, AWGBBurstDelay

10165 
10166  BAWGBAmpl(0)
10167  BAWGBOffset(0)
10168  BAWGBFreq(0)
10169  BAWGBPhase(0)
10170  BAWGBDutyCycle(0)
10171 
10172  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
10173  if AWG_2X.get() == 2:
10174  AWGBperiodvalue = (BaseSampleRate*2)/AWGBFreqvalue
10175  SamplesPermS = int((BaseSampleRate*2)/1000) # 200
10176  else:
10177  AWGBperiodvalue = BaseSampleRate/AWGBFreqvalue
10178  SamplesPermS = int(BaseSampleRate/1000) # 100
10179  else:
10180  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
10181  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
10182  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
10183  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10184  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)
10185  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)
10186  else:
10187  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
10188  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue

10190  PulseWidth = int(AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBDutyCyclevalue / 2)
10191  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10192  DelayValue = int(AWGBperiodvalue*(AWGBPhasevalue/360))
10193  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10194  DelayValue = int(AWGBPhasevalue*SamplesPermS)
10195  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
10196  AWGBwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2)
10197  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10198  AWGBwaveform.append(MaxV)
10199  for i in range(PulseWidth):
10200  AWGBwaveform.append(MinV)
10201  DelayValue = int(AWGBperiodvalue-DelayValue)
10202  for i in range(DelayValue-PulseWidth):
10203  AWGBwaveform.append((MinV+MaxV)/2)
10204  if AWGBBurstFlag.get() == 1:
10205  TempOneCycle = AWGBwaveform
10206  for i in range(AWGBCycles-1):
10207  AWGBwaveform = numpy.concatenate((AWGBwaveform, TempOneCycle))
10208  TempDelay = int(AWGBBurstDelay*SamplesPermS) # convert mS to samples
10209  AWGBwaveform = numpy.pad(AWGBwaveform, (TempDelay, 0), 'edge')
10210  SplitAWGBwaveform()

10256 def AWGBMakeUGNoise():

10318 def UpdateAWGB():
10319  global AWGBAmplvalue, AWGBOffsetvalue, AWGA2X, AWG_2X
10320  global AWGBFreqvalue, AWGBPhasevalue, AWGBPhaseDelay
10321  global AWGBDutyCyclevalue, FSweepMode, AWGBRepeatFlag, AWGSync
10322  global AWGBWave, AWGBMode, AWGBTerm, AWGBwaveform, AWGBIOMode
10323  global CHA, CHB, AWGSAMPLErate, DevID, devx, HWRevOne
10324  global amp2lab, off2lab, AWG_Amp_Mode # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10325  global AWGA2X, AWGB2X, AWGAWave, AWGARepeatFlag
10326 
10327  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 0: # 0 = Min/Max mode, 1 = Amp/Offset
10328  amp2lab.config(text = "Min Ch B" ) # change displayed value
10329  off2lab.config(text = "Max Ch B" ) # change displayed value
10330  else:
10331  amp2lab.config(text = "Amp Ch B" )
10332  off2lab.config(text = "Off Ch B" )
10333 #
10334  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10335  AWGBWave = 'arbitrary'
10336  if AWGBFreqvalue > 0.0:
10337  AWGBperiodvalue = AWGSAMPLErate/AWGBFreqvalue
10338  else:
10339  AWGBperiodvalue = 0.0
10340 #
10341  if AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 0:
10342  if AWGBWave == 'square':
10343  AWGBPhasevalue = AWGBPhasevalue + 270.0
10344  if AWGBPhasevalue > 359:
10345  AWGBPhasevalue = AWGBPhasevalue - 360
10346  if AWGBPhasevalue > 0:
10347  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBperiodvalue * AWGBPhasevalue / 360.0
10348  else:
10349  AWGBdelayvalue = 0.0
10350  elif AWGBPhaseDelay.get() == 1:
10351  AWGBdelayvalue = AWGBPhasevalue * 100
10352 #
10353  if AWGBTerm.get() == 0: # Open termination
10354  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
10355  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
10356  elif AWGBTerm.get() == 1: # 50 Ohm termination to GND
10357  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to open
10358  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to closed
10359  elif AWGBTerm.get() == 2: # 50 Ohm termination to +2.5 Volts
10360  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x50, 37, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set 2.5 V switch to closed
10361  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 38, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set GND switch to open
10362 
10363  if AWGBWave == 'dc':
10364  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10365  AWGBWave == 'arbitrary'
10366  CHB.arbitrary(AWGA2X, AWGARepeatFlag.get())
10367  else:
10368  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
10369  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10370  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHB in SVMI mode
10371  else:
10372  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHB in SVMI split mode
10373  CHB.constant(AWGBOffsetvalue)
10374  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure Voltage mode
10375  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10376  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHB in SIMV mode
10377  else:
10378  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHB in SIMV split mode
10379  CHB.constant(AWGBOffsetvalue/1000)
10380  if AWGBMode.get() == 2: # Hi impedance mode
10381  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10382  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
10383  else:
10384  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
10385 #
10386  if AWGBIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
10387  if HWRevOne == "D":
10388  AWGBMode.set(1)
10389  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode
10390 #
10391  else:
10392  if AWGBMode.get() == 0: # Source Voltage measure current mode
10393  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10394  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI # Put CHB in SVMI mode
10395  else:
10396  CHB.mode = Mode.SVMI_SPLIT # Put CHB in SVMI split mode
10397  if AWGBMode.get() == 1: # Source current measure Voltage mode
10398  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10399  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV # Put CHB in SIMV mode
10400  else:
10401  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # Put CHB in SIMV split mode
10402  AWGBOffsetvalue = AWGBOffsetvalue/1000
10403  AWGBAmplvalue = AWGBAmplvalue/1000
10404  if AWGBMode.get() == 2: # Hi impedance mode
10405  if AWGBIOMode.get() == 0:
10406  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z # Put CHB in Hi Z mode
10407  else:
10408  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
10409  else:
10410  if AWG_Amp_Mode.get() == 1:
10411  MaxV = (AWGBOffsetvalue+AWGBAmplvalue)
10412  MinV = (AWGBOffsetvalue-AWGBAmplvalue)
10413  else:
10414  MaxV = AWGBOffsetvalue
10415  MinV = AWGBAmplvalue
10416  try: # keep going even if low level library returns an error
10417  if AWGBWave == 'sine':
10418  CHB.sine(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
10419  elif AWGBWave == 'triangle':
10420  CHB.triangle(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
10421  elif AWGBWave == 'sawtooth':
10422  CHB.sawtooth(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
10423  elif AWGBWave == 'square':
10424  CHB.square(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue, AWGBDutyCyclevalue)
10425  elif AWGBWave == 'stairstep':
10426  CHB.stairstep(MaxV, MinV, AWGBperiodvalue, AWGBdelayvalue)
10427  elif AWGBWave == 'arbitrary':
10428  if AWGSync.get() == 0:
10429  AWGBRepeatFlag.set(1)
10430  if AWG_2X.get() == 1:
10431  AWGBWave == 'arbitrary'
10432  CHB.arbitrary(AWGA2X, AWGARepeatFlag.get())
10433  else:
10434  CHB.arbitrary(AWGBwaveform, AWGBRepeatFlag.get()) # set repeat flag
10435  except:
10436  donothing()
10437  if AWGBIOMode.get() > 0: # Split Input / Output mode
10438  if HWRevOne == "D":
10439  AWGBMode.set(1)
10440  CHB.mode = Mode.SIMV_SPLIT # channel must be in source current mode

10447  session.end()
10448  BAWGEnab() # set-up new AWG settings

10450  session.start(0)

10646 def BCSVfile(): # Store the trace as CSV file [frequency, magnitude or dB value]
10647  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep, FBins, bodewindow
10648  global SAMPLErate, ShowCA_VdB, ShowCA_P, ShowCB_VdB, ShowCB_P
10649 
10650  # Set the TRACEsize variable
10651  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
10652  TRACEsize = len(FSweepAdB) # Set the trace length
10653  elif ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
10654  TRACEsize = len(FSweepBdB)
10655  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
10656  return()
10657 # ask if save as magnitude or dB
10658  dB = askyesno("Mag or dB: ","Save amplidude data as dB (Yes) or Mag (No):\n", parent=bodewindow)
10659 # Yes 1 = dB, No 0 = Mag
10660  # Make the file name and open it
10661  tme = strftime("%Y%b%d-%H%M%S", gmtime()) # The time
10662  filename = "Bode-" + tme
10663  filename = filename + ".csv"
10664  # open file to save data
10665  filename = asksaveasfilename(initialfile = filename, defaultextension = ".csv",
10666  filetypes=[("Comma Separated Values", "*.csv")], parent=bodewindow)
10667  DataFile = open(filename,'a') # Open output file
10668  HeaderString = 'Frequency-#, '
10669  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
10670  if dB == 1:
10671  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-dB, '
10672  if dB == 0:
10673  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CA-Mag, '
10674  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
10675  if dB == 1:
10676  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-dB, '
10677  if dB == 0:
10678  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'CB-Mag, '
10679  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
10680  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase A-B, '
10681  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
10682  HeaderString = HeaderString + 'Phase B-A, '
10683  HeaderString = HeaderString + '\n'
10684  DataFile.write( HeaderString )
10685 
10686  n = 0
10687  while n < len(FSweepAdB):
10688  F = FBins[FStep[n]] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
10689  txt = str(F)
10690  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
10691  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
10692  if dB == 0:
10693  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
10694  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
10695  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
10696  V = 10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17 # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB
10697  if dB == 0:
10698  V = 10.0**(V/20.0)
10699  txt = txt + "," + str(V)
10700  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
10701  RelPhase = FSweepAPh[n]#-FSweepBPh[n]
10702  if RelPhase > 180:
10703  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
10704  elif RelPhase < -180:
10705  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
10706  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
10707  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
10708  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[n]#-FSweepAPh[n]
10709  if RelPhase > 180:
10710  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
10711  elif RelPhase < -180:
10712  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
10713  txt = txt + "," + str(RelPhase)
10714  txt = txt + "\n"
10715  DataFile.write(txt)
10716  n = n + 1
10717 
10718  DataFile.close() # Close the file
10719

10766  try:

10906 def BStartBP():
10907  global RUNstatus, LoopNum, PowerStatus, devx, PwrBt, bodewindow, session, AWGSync
10908  global ShowCA_VdB, ShowCB_P, ShowCB_VdB, ShowCB_P, ShowMathBP, contloop, discontloop
10909  global FBins, FStep, NSteps, FSweepMode, HScaleBP, CutDC
10910  global AWGAMode, AWGAShape, AWGBMode, AWGBShape
10911  global StartBodeEntry, StopBodeEntry, SweepStepBodeEntry, DevID, FWRevOne
10912  global AWGAFreqEntry, AWGBFreqEntry, Reset_Freq, AWGAIOMode, AWGBIOMode
10913  global Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, AWG_2X, ZEROstuffing, SAMPLErate
10914  global BeginIndex, EndIndex
10915 
10916  if DevID == "No Device":
10917  showwarning("WARNING","No Device Plugged In!")
10918  elif FWRevOne == 0.0:
10919  showwarning("WARNING","Out of data Firmware!")
10920  else:
10921  if PowerStatus == 0:
10922  PowerStatus = 1
10923  PwrBt.config(style="Pwr.TButton",text="PWR-On")
10924  devx.ctrl_transfer( 0x40, 0x51, 49, 0, 0, 0, 100) # turn on analog power
10925 
10926  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 0 and ShowCB_VdB.get() == 0 and ShowMathBP.get() == 0:
10927  showwarning("WARNING","Select at least one trace first", parent=bodewindow)
10928  return()
10929  #
10930  if ZEROstuffing.get() < 3:
10931  ZEROstuffing.set(3)
10932  CutDC.set(1) # set to remove DC
10933  try:
10934  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
10935  except:
10936  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
10937  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)
10938  EndFreq = 10000
10939  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
10940  if EndFreq >= 20000:
10941  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
10942  FBins = numpy.linspace(0, 100000, num=16384)
10943  else:
10944  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
10945  FBins = numpy.linspace(0, 50000, num=16384)
10946  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
10947  SetADC_Mux()
10948  try:
10949  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
10950  except:
10951  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
10952  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
10953  BeginFreq = 100
10954  #
10955  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
10956  if AWGAMode.get() == 2:
10957  AWGAMode.set(0) # Set AWG A to SVMI
10958  AWGAShape.set(18) # Set Shape to Sine
10959  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
10960  AWGBIOMode.set(1)
10961  AWGBMode.set(0)
10962  else:
10963  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
10964  AWG_2X.set(0)
10965  BAWG2X()
10966  Reset_Freq = AWGAFreqEntry.get()
10967  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
10968  if AWGBMode.get() == 2:
10969  AWGBMode.set(0) # Set AWG B to SVMI
10970  AWGBShape.set(18) # Set Shape to Sine
10971  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
10972  AWGAIOMode.set(1)
10973  AWGAMode.set(0)
10974  else:
10975  AWGAMode.set(2) # Set AWG A to Hi-Z
10976  AWG_2X.set(0)
10977  BAWG2X()
10978  Reset_Freq = AWGBFreqEntry.get()
10979  if FSweepMode.get() == 3: # using external Minigen
10980  AWGAMode.set(2) # Set AWG A to Hi-Z
10981  AWGBMode.set(2) # Set AWG B to Hi-Z
10982  try:
10983  NSteps.set(float(SweepStepBodeEntry.get()))
10984  except:
10985  SweepStepBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
10986  SweepStepBodeEntry.insert(0, NSteps.get())
10987  #
10988  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
10989  LoopNum.set(1)
10990  NyquistFreq = SAMPLErate/2
10991  BeginIndex = int((BeginFreq/NyquistFreq)*16384)
10992  EndIndex = int((EndFreq/NyquistFreq)*16384)
10993  if NSteps.get() < 5:
10994  NSteps.set(5)
10995  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
10996  LogFStop = math.log10(EndIndex)
10997  try:
10998  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginIndex)
10999  except:
11000  LogFStart = 1.0
11001  FStep = numpy.logspace(LogFStart, LogFStop, num=NSteps.get(), base=10.0)
11002  else:
11003  FStep = numpy.linspace(BeginIndex, EndIndex, num=NSteps.get())
11004  BStart()
11005  # UpdateBodeAll() # Always Update
11006 #

11012  AWGAFreqEntry.insert(0, Reset_Freq)

11015  AWGBFreqEntry.insert(0, Reset_Freq)

11024  RUNstatus.set(3)

11026  RUNstatus.set(3)

11135 def DoFFT(): # Fast Fourier transformation
11136  global FFTBuffA, FFTBuffB
11137  global ShowC1_VdB, ShowC1_P, ShowC2_VdB, ShowC2_P
11138  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA, FFTresultAB, PhaseAB
11139  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB
11140  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh
11141  global PhaseA, PhaseB, PhaseMemoryA, PhaseMemoryB
11142  global FFTwindowshape, FFTbandwidth
11143  global AWGSAMPLErate, StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry, StartBodeEntry
11144  global SMPfft, LoopNum, IA_Ext_Conf
11145  global STARTsample, STOPsample
11146  global TRACEaverage, FreqTraceMode, FSweepMode
11147  global TRACEresetFreq, ZEROstuffing
11148  global SpectrumScreenStatus, IAScreenStatus, BodeScreenStatus
11149  global NetworkScreenStatus, NSweepSeriesR, NSweepSeriesX, NSweepSeriesMag, NSweepSeriesAng
11150 
11151  # T1 = time.time() # For time measurement of FFT routine
11152  REX = []
11153  PhaseA = []
11154  PhaseB = []
11155  # Convert list to numpy array REX for faster Numpy calculations
11156  # Take the first fft samples
11157  REX = numpy.array(FFTBuffA[0:SMPfft]) # Make a numpy arry of the list
11158 
11159  # Set Analog level display value MAX value is 5 volts for ALM1000
11160  REX = REX / 5.0
11161 
11162  # Do the FFT window function
11163  REX = REX * FFTwindowshape[0:len(REX)] # The windowing shape function only over the samples
11164 
11165  # Zero stuffing of array for better interpolation of peak level of signals
11166  ZEROstuffingvalue = int(2 ** ZEROstuffing.get())
11167  fftsamples = ZEROstuffingvalue * SMPfft # Add zero's to the arrays
11168 
11169  # Save previous trace in memory for max or average trace
11170  FFTmemoryA = FFTresultA
11171  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
11172  PhaseMemoryA = PhaseA
11173 
11174  # FFT with numpy
11175  ALL = numpy.fft.fft(REX, n=fftsamples) # Do FFT + zerostuffing till n=fftsamples with NUMPY ALL = Real + Imaginary part
11176  PhaseA = numpy.angle(ALL, deg=True) # calculate angle
11177  ALL = numpy.absolute(ALL) # Make absolute SQR(REX*REX + IMX*IMX) for VOLTAGE!
11178  ALL = ALL * ALL # Convert from Voltage to Power (P = (V*V) / R; R = 1)
11179 
11180  le = int(len(ALL) / 2) # Only half is used, other half is mirror
11181  ALL = ALL[0:le] # So take only first half of the array
11182  PhaseA = PhaseA[0:le]
11183  Totalcorr = float(ZEROstuffingvalue)/ fftsamples # For VOLTAGE!
11184  Totalcorr = Totalcorr * Totalcorr # For POWER!
11185  FFTresultA = Totalcorr * ALL
11186 #
11187  REX = []
11188  # Convert list to numpy array REX for faster Numpy calculations
11189  # Take the first fft samples
11190  REX = numpy.array(FFTBuffB[0:SMPfft]) # Make a numpy arry of the list
11191 
11192  # Set level display value MAX value is 5 volts for ALM1000
11193  REX = REX / 5.0
11194 
11195  # Do the FFT window function
11196  try:
11197  REX = REX * FFTwindowshape # The windowing shape function only over the samples
11198  except:
11199  return
11200  # Zero stuffing of array for better interpolation of peak level of signals
11201  ZEROstuffingvalue = int(2 ** ZEROstuffing.get())
11202  fftsamples = ZEROstuffingvalue * SMPfft # Add zero's to the arrays
11203 
11204  # Save previous trace in memory for max or average trace
11205  FFTmemoryB = FFTresultB
11206  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
11207  PhaseMemoryB = PhaseB
11208  # FFT with numpy
11209  ALL = numpy.fft.fft(REX, n=fftsamples) # Do FFT + zerostuffing till n=fftsamples with NUMPY ALL = Real + Imaginary part
11210  PhaseB = numpy.angle(ALL, deg=True) # calculate angle
11211  ALL = numpy.absolute(ALL) # Make absolute SQR(REX*REX + IMX*IMX) for VOLTAGE!
11212  ALL = ALL * ALL # Convert from Voltage to Power (P = (U*U) / R; R = 1)
11213 
11214  le = int(len(ALL) / 2 ) # Only half is used, other half is mirror
11215  ALL = ALL[0:le] # So take only first half of the array
11216  PhaseB = PhaseB[0:le]
11217  Totalcorr = float(ZEROstuffingvalue)/ fftsamples # For VOLTAGE!
11218  Totalcorr = Totalcorr * Totalcorr # For POWER!
11219  FFTresultB = Totalcorr * ALL
11220 #
11221  if IA_Ext_Conf.get() == 1: # calculate fft for voltage A-B for use if IA set to config 2
11222  REX = []
11223  PhaseAB = []
11224  # Convert list to numpy array REX for faster Numpy calculations
11225  # Take the first fft samples
11226  REX = numpy.array(FFTBuffA[0:SMPfft]-FFTBuffB[0:SMPfft]) # Make a numpy arry of the VA-VB list
11227 
11228  # Set level display value MAX value is 5 volts for ALM1000
11229  REX = REX / 5.0
11230 
11231  # Do the FFT window function
11232  REX = REX * FFTwindowshape # The windowing shape function only over the samples
11233 
11234  # Zero stuffing of array for better interpolation of peak level of signals
11235  ZEROstuffingvalue = int(2 ** ZEROstuffing.get())
11236  fftsamples = ZEROstuffingvalue * SMPfft # Add zero's to the arrays
11237 
11238  # Save previous trace in memory for max or average trace
11239  # FFTmemoryB = FFTresultB
11240  # if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3:
11241  # PhaseMemoryB = PhaseB
11242  # FFT with numpy
11243  ALL = numpy.fft.fft(REX, n=fftsamples) # Do FFT + zerostuffing till n=fftsamples with NUMPY ALL = Real + Imaginary part
11244  PhaseAB = numpy.angle(ALL, deg=True) # calculate angle
11245  ALL = numpy.absolute(ALL) # Make absolute SQR(REX*REX + IMX*IMX) for VOLTAGE!
11246  ALL = ALL * ALL # Convert from Voltage to Power (P = (U*U) / R; R = 1)
11247 
11248  le = len(ALL) / 2 # Only half is used, other half is mirror
11249  ALL = ALL[:le] # So take only first half of the array
11250  PhaseAB = PhaseAB[:le]
11251  Totalcorr = float(ZEROstuffingvalue)/ fftsamples # For VOLTAGE!
11252  Totalcorr = Totalcorr * Totalcorr # For POWER!
11253  FFTresultAB = Totalcorr * ALL
11254 #
11255  TRACEsize = int(len(FFTresultB))
11256  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1)
11257  if SpectrumScreenStatus.get() > 0:
11258  try:
11259  StartFrequency = float(StartFreqEntry.get())
11260  except:
11261  StartFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11262  StartFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
11263  StartFrequency = 100
11264  STARTsample = StartFrequency / Fsample
11265  else:
11266  STARTsample = 0.0
11267  if LoopNum.get() == 1:
11268  PhaseMemoryB = PhaseB
11269  FSweepAdB = []
11270  FSweepBdB = []
11271  FSweepAPh = []
11272  FSweepBPh = []
11273  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:
11274  NSweepSeriesR = []
11275  NSweepSeriesX = []
11276  NSweepSeriesMag = [] # in ohms
11277  NSweepSeriesAng = [] # in degrees
11278  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 1: # Normal mode 1, do not change
11279  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
11280  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultA[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11281  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11282  STARTsample = ptmax
11283  i = 0
11284  while i < 6:
11285  PhaseMemoryB[ptmax+i] = PhaseB[ptmax]
11286  i = i + 1
11287  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
11288  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultB[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11289  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11290  STARTsample = ptmax
11291  i = 0
11292  while i < 6:
11293  PhaseMemoryB[ptmax+i] = PhaseB[ptmax]
11294  i = i + 1
11295 
11296  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 2 and TRACEresetFreq == False: # Peak hold mode 2, change v to peak value
11297  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
11298  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultA[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11299  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11300  STARTsample = ptmax
11301  i = 0
11302  while i < 6:
11303  PhaseMemoryB[ptmax+i] = PhaseB[ptmax]
11304  i = i + 1
11305  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
11306  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultB[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11307  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11308  STARTsample = ptmax
11309  i = 0
11310  while i < 6:
11311  PhaseMemoryB[ptmax+i] = PhaseB[ptmax]
11312  i = i + 1
11313  if len(FFTresultB) == len(FFTmemoryB):
11314  FFTresultB = numpy.maximum(FFTresultB, FFTmemoryB)#
11315  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3 and TRACEresetFreq == False: # Average mode 3, add difference / TRACEaverage to v
11316  try:
11317  FFTresultB = FFTmemoryB + (FFTresultB - FFTmemoryB) / TRACEaverage.get()
11318  PhaseB = PhaseMemoryB +(PhaseB - PhaseMemoryB) / TRACEaverage.get()
11319  except:
11320  FFTmemoryB = FFTresultB
11321  PhaseMemoryB = PhaseB
11322 #
11323  TRACEsize = int(len(FFTresultA))
11324  Fsample = float(AWGSAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1)
11325  if SpectrumScreenStatus.get() > 0:
11326  STARTsample = StartFrequency / Fsample
11327  else:
11328  STARTsample = 0.0
11329  if LoopNum.get() == 1:
11330  PhaseMemoryA = PhaseA
11331  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 1: # Normal mode 1, do not change
11332  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
11333  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultA[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11334  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11335  STARTsample = ptmax
11336  i = 0
11337  while i < 6:
11338  PhaseMemoryA[ptmax+i] = PhaseA[ptmax]
11339  i = i + 1
11340  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
11341  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultB[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11342  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11343  STARTsample = ptmax
11344  i = 0
11345  while i < 6:
11346  PhaseMemoryA[ptmax+i] = PhaseA[ptmax]
11347  i = i + 1
11348 
11349  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 2 and TRACEresetFreq == False: # Peak hold mode 2, change v to peak value
11350  if FSweepMode.get() == 1:
11351  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultA[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11352  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11353  STARTsample = ptmax
11354  i = 0
11355  while i < 6:
11356  PhaseMemoryA[ptmax+i] = PhaseA[ptmax]
11357  i = i + 1
11358  if FSweepMode.get() == 2:
11359  ptmax = numpy.argmax(FFTresultB[STARTsample:TRACEsize])
11360  if ptmax > STARTsample:
11361  STARTsample = ptmax
11362  i = 0
11363  while i < 6:
11364  PhaseMemoryA[ptmax+i] = PhaseA[ptmax]
11365  i = i + 1
11366 #
11367  if len(FFTresultA) == len(FFTmemoryA):
11368  FFTresultA = numpy.maximum(FFTresultA, FFTmemoryA)
11369  if FreqTraceMode.get() == 3 and TRACEresetFreq == False: # Average mode 3, add difference / TRACEaverage to v
11370  try:
11371  FFTresultA = FFTmemoryA + (FFTresultA - FFTmemoryA) / TRACEaverage.get()
11372  PhaseA = PhaseMemoryA +(PhaseA - PhaseMemoryA) / TRACEaverage.get()
11373  except:
11374  FFTmemoryA = FFTresultA
11375  PhaseMemoryA = PhaseA
11376 #
11377  if FSweepMode.get() > 0 and BodeScreenStatus.get() > 0:
11378  FSweepAdB.append(numpy.amax(FFTresultA))
11379  FSweepBdB.append(numpy.amax(FFTresultB))
11380  FSweepAPh.append(PhaseA[numpy.argmax(FFTresultA)])
11381  FSweepBPh.append(PhaseB[numpy.argmax(FFTresultB)])
11382 
11383  TRACEresetFreq = False # Trace reset done

11385 def MakeFreqTrace(): # Update the grid and trace
11386  global FFTmemoryA, FFTresultA
11387  global FFTmemoryB, FFTresultB
11388  global PhaseA, PhaseB, PhaseMemoryA, PhaseMemoryB
11389  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep
11390  global ShowC1_VdB, ShowC1_P, ShowC2_VdB, ShowC2_P, ShowMathSA
11391  global PeakxA, PeakyA, PeakxB, PeakyB, PeakdbA, PeakdbB
11392  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM, PeakIndexA, PeakIndexB
11393  global PeakfreqA, PeakfreqB, Two_X_Sample
11394  global DBdivindex # Index value
11395  global DBdivlist # dB per division list
11396  global DBlevel # Reference level
11397  global GRHF,GRWF # Screenheight, Screenwidth
11398  global AWGSAMPLErate, HScale, Fsample, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
11399  global StartFreqEntry, StopFreqEntry, PhCenFreqEntry, RelPhaseCenter
11400  global STARTsample, STOPsample, LoopNum, FSweepMode
11401  global FreqTraceMode
11402  global T1Fline, T2Fline, TFMline, T1Pline, T2Pline
11403  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
11404  global X0LF, Y0TF # Left top X value, Left top Y value
11405 
11406  # Set the TRACEsize variable
11407  TRACEsize = 0
11408  try:
11409  StartFrequency = float(StartFreqEntry.get())
11410  except:
11411  StartFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11412  StartFreqEntry.insert(0,100)
11413  StartFrequency = 100
11414  try:
11415  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
11416  except:
11417  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11418  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
11419  StopFrequency = 50000
11420  if StartFrequency > StopFrequency :
11421  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11422  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
11423  StopFrequency = 50000
11424  if StopFrequency < StartFrequency :
11425  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11426  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
11427  StopFrequency = 50000
11428  try:
11429  Phasecenter = int(PhCenFreqEntry.get())
11430  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
11431  except:
11432  PhCenFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
11433  PhCenFreqEntry.insert(0,0)
11434  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
11435  Phasecenter = 0
11436  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
11437  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultA) # Set the trace length
11438  elif ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
11439  TRACEsize = len(FFTresultB)
11440  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
11441  return()
11442  if FSweepMode.get() > 0 and LoopNum.get() == NSteps.get():
11443  PhaseA = PhaseMemoryA
11444  PhaseB = PhaseMemoryB
11445  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
11446  Yconv = float(GRHF) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindex.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
11447  Yc = float(Y0TF) + Yconv * (DBlevel.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
11448  Ymin = Y0TF # Minimum position of screen grid (top)
11449  Ymax = Y0TF + GRHF # Maximum position of screen grid (bottom)
11450  Yphconv = float(GRHF) / 360
11451  Yp = float(Y0TF) + Yphconv + 180
11452  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
11453  Fpixel = (StopFrequency - StartFrequency) / GRWF # Frequency step per screen pixel
11454  Fsample = float(SAMPLErate / 2) / (TRACEsize - 1) # Frequency step per sample
11455  LogFStop = math.log10(StopFrequency)
11456  try:
11457  LogFStart = math.log10(StartFrequency)
11458  except:
11459  LogFStart = 0.0
11460  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWF
11461  STARTsample = StartFrequency / Fsample # First sample in FFTresult[] that is used
11462  STARTsample = int(math.ceil(STARTsample)) # First within screen range
11463 
11464  STOPsample = StopFrequency / Fsample # Last sample in FFTresult[] that is used
11465  STOPsample = int(math.floor(STOPsample)) # Last within screen range, math.floor actually not necessary, part of int
11466 
11467  MAXsample = TRACEsize # Just an out of range check
11468  if STARTsample > (MAXsample - 1):
11469  STARTsample = MAXsample - 1
11470 
11471  if STOPsample > MAXsample:
11472  STOPsample = MAXsample
11473 
11474  T1Fline = []
11475  T2Fline = []
11476  T1Pline = []
11477  T2Pline = []
11478  TFMline = []
11479  n = STARTsample
11480  PeakIndexA = PeakIndexB = n
11481  PeakdbA = PeakdbB = PeakMdb = -200 # PeakdbB
11482  while n <= STOPsample:
11483  F = n * Fsample
11484  if HScale.get() == 1:
11485  try:
11486  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
11487  x = X0LF + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
11488  except:
11489  x = X0LF
11490  else:
11491  x = X0LF + (F - StartFrequency) / Fpixel
11492  if ShowC1_VdB.get() == 1:
11493  T1Fline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11494  try:
11495  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
11496  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11497  except:
11498  ya = Ymax
11499  if (ya < Ymin):
11500  ya = Ymin
11501  if (ya > Ymax):
11502  ya = Ymax
11503  if dbA > PeakdbA:
11504  PeakdbA = dbA
11505  PeakyA = int(ya + 0.5)
11506  PeakxA = int(x + 0.5)
11507  PeakfreqA = F
11508  PeakIndexA = n
11509  T1Fline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11510  if ShowC2_VdB.get() == 1:
11511  T2Fline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11512  try:
11513  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11514  yb = Yc - Yconv * dbB
11515  except:
11516  yb = Ymax
11517  if (yb < Ymin):
11518  yb = Ymin
11519  if (yb > Ymax):
11520  yb = Ymax
11521  if dbB > PeakdbB:
11522  PeakdbB = dbB
11523  PeakyB = int(yb + 0.5)
11524  PeakxB = int(x + 0.5)
11525  PeakfreqB = F
11526  PeakIndexB = n
11527  T2Fline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
11528  if ShowC1_P.get() == 1:
11529  T1Pline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11530  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
11531  RelPhase = PhaseMemoryA[n]-PhaseMemoryB[n]
11532  else:
11533  RelPhase = PhaseA[n]-PhaseB[n]
11534  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
11535  if RelPhase > 180:
11536  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
11537  elif RelPhase < -180:
11538  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
11539  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
11540  PhErr = 0.0018 * n * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
11541  RelPhase = RelPhase + PhErr - 12.0
11542  else:
11543  RelPhase = RelPhase - 9.0
11544  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
11545  T1Pline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11546  if ShowC2_P.get() == 1:
11547  T2Pline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11548  if FSweepMode.get() > 0:
11549  RelPhase = PhaseMemoryB[n]-PhaseMemoryA[n]
11550  else:
11551  RelPhase = PhaseB[n]-PhaseA[n]
11552  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
11553  if RelPhase > 180:
11554  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
11555  elif RelPhase < -180:
11556  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
11557  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
11558  PhErr = 0.0018 * n * Fsample # calculate pahse error due half sample period offset
11559  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr - 12.0
11560  else:
11561  RelPhase = RelPhase - 9.0
11562  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
11563  T2Pline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11564  if ShowMathSA.get() > 0:
11565  TFMline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11566  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultA[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
11567  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FFTresultB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11568  if ShowMathSA.get() == 1:
11569  MdB = dbA - dbB
11570  elif ShowMathSA.get() == 2:
11571  MdB = dbB - dbA
11572  yb = Yc - Yconv * MdB
11573  if (yb < Ymin):
11574  yb = Ymin
11575  if (yb > Ymax):
11576  yb = Ymax
11577  if MdB > PeakMdb:
11578  PeakMdb = MdB
11579  PeakyM = int(yb + 0.5)
11580  PeakxM = int(x + 0.5)
11581  PeakfreqM = F
11582  TFMline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
11583  n = n + 1
11584 # make Bode Plot Traces
11585 def MakeBodeTrace(): # Update the grid and trace
11586  global FSweepAdB, FSweepBdB, FSweepAPh, FSweepBPh, FStep, FBins
11587  global ShowCA_VdB, ShowCA_P, ShowCB_VdB, ShowCB_P, ShowMathBP
11588  global PeakxA, PeakyA, PeakxB, PeakyB, PeakdbA, PeakdbB
11589  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM
11590  global PeakfreqA, PeakfreqB, Two_X_Sample, PhaseOffset1x, PhaseOffset2x
11591  global DBdivindexBP # Index value
11592  global DBdivlist # dB per division list
11593  global DBlevelBP # Reference level
11594  global GRHBP # Screenheight
11595  global GRWBP # Screenwidth
11596  global AWGSAMPLErate, HScaleBP, RUNstatus, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate
11597  global StartBodeEntry, StopBodeEntry
11598  global STARTsample, STOPsample, LoopNum, FSweepMode
11599  global FreqTraceMode, RelPhaseCenter, PhCenBodeEntry, ImCenBodeEntry, ImpedanceCenter, Impedcenter
11600  global TAFline, TBFline, TBPMline, TAPline, TBPline
11601  global Vdiv # Number of vertical divisions
11602  global X0LBP # Left top X value
11603  global Y0TBP # Left top Y value
11604  global ResScale, NetworkScreenStatus, Show_Rseries, NSweepSeriesR, Show_Xseries, NSweepSeriesX
11605  global Show_Magnitude, NSweepSeriesMag, Show_Angle, NSweepSeriesAng
11606  global TIARline, TIAXline, TIAMagline, TIAAngline, CurrentFreqX
11607 
11608  # Set the TRACEsize variable
11609  TRACEsize = 0
11610  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
11611  TRACEsize = len(FStep) # Set the trace length
11612  elif ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1 or ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
11613  TRACEsize = len(FStep)
11614  if TRACEsize == 0: # If no trace, skip rest of this routine
11615  return()
11616  #
11617  try:
11618  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
11619  except:
11620  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11621  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)

11623  try:
11624  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
11625  except:
11626  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11627  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
11628  BeginFreq = 100
11629  try:
11630  Phasecenter = int(PhCenBodeEntry.get())
11631  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
11632  except:
11633  PhCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11634  PhCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
11635  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
11636  Phasecenter = 0
11637  try:
11638  Impedcenter = int(ImCenBodeEntry.get())
11639  ImpedanceCenter.set(Impedcenter)
11640  except:
11641  ImCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11642  ImCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
11643  ImpedanceCenter.set(0)
11644  Impedcenter = 0
11645  #
11646  HalfSAMPLErate = SAMPLErate/2
11647  BeginIndex = int((BeginFreq/HalfSAMPLErate)*16384)
11648  EndIndex = int((EndFreq/HalfSAMPLErate)*16384)
11649  CurrentFreqX = X0LBP + 14
11650  if FSweepMode.get() > 0 and len(FSweepAdB) > 4:
11651  # Vertical conversion factors (level dBs) and border limits
11652  Yconv = float(GRHBP) / (Vdiv.get() * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]) # Conversion factors, Yconv is the number of screenpoints per dB
11653  Yc = float(Y0TBP) + Yconv * (DBlevelBP.get()) # Yc is the 0 dBm position, can be outside the screen!
11654  Ymin = Y0TBP # Minimum position of screen grid (top)
11655  Ymax = Y0TBP + GRHBP # Maximum position of screen grid (bottom)
11656  Yphconv = float(GRHBP) / 360 # degrees per pixel
11657  Yp = float(Y0TBP) + Yphconv + 180
11658  x1 = X0LBP + 14
11659  # Horizontal conversion factors (frequency Hz) and border limits
11660  Fpixel = (EndFreq - BeginFreq) / GRWBP # Frequency step per screen pixel
11661  LogFStop = math.log10(EndFreq)
11662  try:
11663  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginFreq)
11664  except:
11665  LogFStart = 0.0
11666  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWBP
11667  TAFline = []
11668  TBFline = []
11669  TAPline = []
11670  TBPline = []
11671  TIARline = []
11672  TIAXline = []
11673  TIAMagline = []
11674  TIAAngline = []
11675  TBPMline = []
11676  PeakdbA = -200
11677  PeakdbB = -200
11678  PeakMdb = -200
11679  n = 0
11680  for n in range(len(FSweepAdB)): # while n < len(FStep):
11681  if n < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
11682  F = FBins[int(FStep[n])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
11683  else:
11684  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
11685  if F >= BeginFreq and F <= EndFreq:
11686  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
11687  try:
11688  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
11689  x = x1 + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
11690  except:
11691  x = x1
11692  else:
11693  x = x1 + (F - BeginFreq) / Fpixel
11694  CurrentFreqX = x
11695  if ShowCA_VdB.get() == 1:
11696  TAFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11697  try:
11698  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
11699  ya = Yc - Yconv * dbA # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11700  except:
11701  ya = Ymax
11702  if (ya < Ymin):
11703  ya = Ymin
11704  if (ya > Ymax):
11705  ya = Ymax
11706  if dbA > PeakdbA:
11707  PeakdbA = dbA
11708  PeakyA = int(ya + 0.5)
11709  PeakxA = int(x + 0.5)
11710  PeakfreqA = F
11711  TAFline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11712  if ShowCB_VdB.get() == 1:
11713  TBFline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11714  try:
11715  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11716  yb = Yc - Yconv * dbB
11717  except:
11718  yb = Ymax
11719  if (yb < Ymin):
11720  yb = Ymin
11721  if (yb > Ymax):
11722  yb = Ymax
11723  if dbB > PeakdbB:
11724  PeakdbB = dbB
11725  PeakyB = int(yb + 0.5)
11726  PeakxB = int(x + 0.5)
11727  PeakfreqB = F
11728  TBFline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
11729  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1:
11730  TAPline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11731  RelPhase = FSweepAPh[n] - FSweepBPh[n]
11732  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
11733  if RelPhase > 180:
11734  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
11735  elif RelPhase < -180:
11736  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
11737  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
11738  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
11739  RelPhase = RelPhase + PhErr - PhaseOffset1x
11740  else:
11741  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhaseOffset2x
11742  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
11743  TAPline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11744  if ShowCB_P.get() == 1:
11745  TBPline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11746  RelPhase = FSweepBPh[n] - FSweepAPh[n]
11747  RelPhase = RelPhase - Phasecenter
11748  if RelPhase > 180:
11749  RelPhase = RelPhase - 360
11750  elif RelPhase < -180:
11751  RelPhase = RelPhase + 360
11752  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 0:
11753  PhErr = 0.0018 * F # calculate phase error due half sample period offset
11754  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhErr - PhaseOffset1x
11755  else:
11756  RelPhase = RelPhase - PhaseOffset2x
11757  ya = Yp - Yphconv * RelPhase
11758  TBPline.append(int(ya + 0.5))
11759  if ShowMathBP.get() > 0:
11760  TBPMline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11761  dbA = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepAdB[n])) + 17) # Convert power to DBs, except for log(0) error
11762  dbB = (10 * math.log10(float(FSweepBdB[n])) + 17) # Add 17 dB for max value of +10 dB ALSO in CSV file routine!
11763  if ShowMathBP.get() == 1:
11764  MdB = dbA - dbB
11765  elif ShowMathBP.get() == 2:
11766  MdB = dbB - dbA
11767  yb = Yc - Yconv * MdB
11768  if (yb < Ymin):
11769  yb = Ymin
11770  if (yb > Ymax):
11771  yb = Ymax
11772  if MdB > PeakMdb:
11773  PeakMdb = MdB
11774  PeakyM = int(yb + 0.5)
11775  PeakxM = int(x + 0.5)
11776  PeakfreqM = F
11777  TBPMline.append(int(yb + 0.5))
11778 # draw impedance trace if necessary
11779  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:
11780  ycenter = Y0TBP + (GRHBP/2)
11781  OhmsperPixel = float(ResScale.get())*Vdiv.get()/GRHBP
11782  n = 0
11783  for n in range(len(NSweepSeriesR)): # while n < len(FStep):
11784  if n < len(FStep): # check if n has gone out off bounds because user did something dumb
11785  F = FBins[int(FStep[n])] # look up frequency bin in list of bins
11786  else:
11787  F = FBins[int(FStep[0])]
11788  if F >= BeginFreq and F <= EndFreq:
11789  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:
11790  try:
11791  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
11792  x = x1 + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
11793  except:
11794  x = x1
11795  else:
11796  x = x1 + (F - BeginFreq) / Fpixel
11797  if Show_Rseries.get() == 1:
11798  TIARline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11799  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesR[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
11800  if (y1 < Ymin):
11801  y1 = Ymin
11802  if (y1 > Ymax):
11803  y1 = Ymax
11804  TIARline.append(y1)
11805  if Show_Xseries.get() == 1:
11806  TIAXline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11807  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesX[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
11808  if (y1 < Ymin):
11809  y1 = Ymin
11810  if (y1 > Ymax):
11811  y1 = Ymax
11812  TIAXline.append(y1)
11813  if Show_Magnitude.get() == 1:
11814  TIAMagline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11815  y1 = ycenter - ((NSweepSeriesMag[n]-Impedcenter) / OhmsperPixel)
11816  if (y1 < Ymin):
11817  y1 = Ymin
11818  if (y1 > Ymax):
11819  y1 = Ymax
11820  TIAMagline.append(y1)
11821  if Show_Angle.get() == 1:
11822  TIAAngline.append(int(x + 0.5))
11823  y1 = ycenter - Yphconv * (NSweepSeriesAng[n]-Phasecenter)
11824  if (y1 < Ymin):
11825  y1 = Ymin
11826  if (y1 > Ymax):
11827  y1 = Ymax
11828  TIAAngline.append(y1)

11830 def MakeBodeScreen(): # Update the screen with traces and text

11833  global PeakxM, PeakyM, PeakMdb, PeakfreqM

11848  global GRHBP # Screenheight

11867

11870  MarkerFreqNum = 0
11871  for n in de:
11872  Bodeca.delete(n)
11873 
11874  try:
11875  EndFreq = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
11876  except:
11877  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11878  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,10000)
11879  EndFreq = 10000
11880  try:
11881  BeginFreq = float(StartBodeEntry.get())
11882  except:
11883  StartBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11884  StartBodeEntry.insert(0,100)
11885  BeginFreq = 100
11886  try:
11887  Phasecenter = int(PhCenBodeEntry.get())
11888  RelPhaseCenter.set(Phasecenter)
11889  except:
11890  PhCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11891  PhCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
11892  RelPhaseCenter.set(0)
11893  Phasecenter = 0
11894  try:
11895  Impedcenter = int(ImCenBodeEntry.get())
11896  ImpedanceCenter.set(Impedcenter)
11897  except:
11898  ImCenBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
11899  ImCenBodeEntry.insert(0,0)
11900  ImpedanceCenter.set(0)
11901  Impedcenter = 0
11902  #
11903  # Draw horizontal grid lines
11904  i = 0
11905  x1 = X0LBP + 14
11906  x2 = x1 + GRWBP
11907  while (i <= Vdiv.get()):
11908  y = Y0TBP + i * GRHBP/Vdiv.get()
11909  Dline = [x1,y,x2,y]
11910  if i == 0 or i == Vdiv.get():
11911  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
11912  else:
11913  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
11914  Vaxis_value = (DBlevelBP.get() - (i * DBdivlist[DBdivindexBP.get()]))
11915  Vaxis_label = str(Vaxis_value)

11917  if ShowCA_P.get() == 1 or ShowCB_P.get() == 1 or Show_Angle.get() == 1:
11918  Vaxis_value = ( 180 - ( i * (360 / Vdiv.get()))) + Phasecenter
11919  Vaxis_label = str(Vaxis_value)
11920  Bodeca.create_text(x2+3, y, text=Vaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace3, anchor="w", font=("arial", FontSize ))
11921  if NetworkScreenStatus.get() > 0:

11926  Vaxis_value = Vaxis_value/1000.0
11927  if Vaxis_value > 5 or Vaxis_value < -5:

11929  else:
11930  Vaxis_label = ' {0:.1f}'.format(Vaxis_value) + 'K'
11931  else:
11932  Vaxis_label = ' {0:.0f} '.format(Vaxis_value)
11933  Bodeca.create_text(x1-23, y, text=Vaxis_label, fill=COLORtrace5, anchor="e", font=("arial", FontSize ))
11934  i = i + 1
11935  # Draw vertical grid lines
11936  i = 0
11937  y1 = Y0TBP
11938  y2 = Y0TBP + GRHBP
11939  if HScaleBP.get() == 1:

11942  try:
11943  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginFreq)
11944  except:
11945  LogFStart = 0.0

11948  while F <= EndFreq:
11949  if F >= BeginFreq:
11950  try:
11951  LogF = math.log10(F) # convet to log Freq
11952  x = x1 + (LogF - LogFStart)/LogFpixel
11953  except:
11954  x = x1

11956  if F == 1 or F == 10 or F == 100 or F == 1000 or F == 10000 or F == 100000:
11957  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
11958  axis_label = str(F)
11959  Bodeca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORgrid, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
11960  else:
11961  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
11962 
11963  if F < 10:
11964  F = F + 1
11965  elif F < 100:
11966  F = F + 10
11967  elif F < 1000:
11968  F = F + 100
11969  elif F < 1000:
11970  F = F + 100
11971  elif F < 10000:
11972  F = F + 1000
11973  elif F < 100000:
11974  F = F + 10000
11975  elif F < 200000:
11976  F = F + 10000
11977  else:
11978  Freqdiv = (EndFreq - BeginFreq) / 10
11979  while (i < 11):
11980  x = x1 + i * GRWBP/10
11981  Dline = [x,y1,x,y2]
11982  if i == 0 or i == 10:
11983  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())
11984  else:
11985  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, dash=(4,3), fill=COLORgrid, width=GridWidth.get())

11987  axis_label = str(axis_value)
11988  Bodeca.create_text(x, y2+3, text=axis_label, fill=COLORgrid, anchor="n", font=("arial", FontSize ))
11989  i = i + 1
11990  # Draw X - Y cursors if needed
11991  Fpixel = (EndFreq - BeginFreq) / GRWBP # Frequency step per screen pixel
11992  LogFStop = math.log10(EndFreq)
11993  try:
11994  LogFStart = math.log10(BeginFreq)
11995  except:
11996  LogFStart = 0.0
11997  LogFpixel = (LogFStop - LogFStart) / GRWBP
11998  if ShowBPCur.get() > 0:
11999  Dline = [BPCursor, Y0TBP, BPCursor, Y0TBP+GRHBP]
12000  Bodeca.create_line(Dline, dash=(3,4), fill=COLORtrigger, width=GridWidth.get())

12004  else:
12005  xfreq = ((BPCursor-x1)*Fpixel)+BeginFreq
