17038 def MakeBoardScreen():
17039  global boardwindow, BoardStatus, session, devx, dev0, dev1, dev2, MultipleBoards
17040  global RevDate, BrdSel, FWRevOne, HWRevOne, FWRevTwo, HWRevTwo, WRevThree, HWRevThree
17041 
17042  if len(session.devices) > 1 and MultipleBoards.get() > 0: # make screen only if more than one board present
17043  if BoardStatus.get() == 0:
17044  BoardStatus.set(1)
17045  boardwindow = Toplevel()
17046  boardwindow.title("Select Board " + RevDate)
17047  boardwindow.resizable(FALSE,FALSE)
17048  boardwindow.protocol("WM_DELETE_WINDOW", DestroyBoardScreen)
17049  toplab = Label(boardwindow,text="- Select ALM1000 -", style="A12B.TLabel")
17050  toplab.pack(side=TOP)
17051  for idx, devx in enumerate(session.devices):
17052  BrdText = "Board # " + str(idx)
17053  if idx == 0:
17054  devx.set_led(0b010) # LED.green
17055  FWRevOne = float(devx.fwver)
17056  HWRevOne = devx.hwver
17057  dev0 = devx #session.devices[0]
17058  brd = Radiobutton(boardwindow, text=BrdText, style="Run.TRadiobutton", variable=BrdSel, value=idx, command=SelectBoard)
17059  elif idx == 1:
17060  devx.set_led(0b100) # LED.blue,
17061  FWRevTwo = float(devx.fwver)
17062  HWRevTwo = devx.hwver
17063  dev1 = devx #session.devices[1]
17064  brd = Radiobutton(boardwindow, text=BrdText, style="Stop.TRadiobutton", variable=BrdSel, value=idx, command=SelectBoard)
17065  elif idx == 2:
17066  devx.set_led(0b001) # LED.red,
17067  FWRevThree = float(devx.fwver)
17068  HWRevThree = devx.hwver
17069  dev2 = devx #session.devices[2]
17070  brd = Radiobutton(boardwindow, text=BrdText, variable=BrdSel, value=idx, command=SelectBoard)
17071  else:
17072  dev3 = session.devices[3]
17073  brd = Radiobutton(boardwindow, text=BrdText, variable=BrdSel, value=idx, command=SelectBoard)
17074  brd.pack(side=TOP)
17075  else:
17076  devx = session.devices[0]
17077  # devx.ignore_dataflow = True
17078  #devx.set_led(0b010) # LED.green
17079  try:
17080  FWRevOne = float(devx.fwver)
17081  HWRevOne = devx.hwver
17082  except:
17083  FWRevOne = "Before 2.06"
17084  HWRevOne = "?"
17085  dev0 = session.devices[0]

17093 def ConnectDevice():
17094  global devx, dev0, dev1, dev2, session, BrdSel, CHA, CHB, DevID, MaxSamples, AWGSAMPLErate
17095  global bcon, FWRevOne, HWRevOne, FWRevTwo, HWRevTwo, WRevThree, HWRevThree, SAMPLErate, MultipleBoards
17096 
17097  if DevID == "No Device" or DevID == "m1k":
17098  #print("Request sample rate: " + str(SAMPLErate))
17099  session = Session(ignore_dataflow=True, sample_rate=SAMPLErate, queue_size=MaxSamples)
17100  # session.add_all()
17101  # SAMPLErate = 200000 #AWGSAMPLErate # Scope sample rate
17102  if not session.devices:
17103  print 'No Device plugged IN!'
17104  DevID = "No Device"
17105  FWRevOne = 0.0
17106  bcon.configure(text="Recon", style="RConn.TButton")
17107  return
17108  session.configure(sample_rate=SAMPLErate)
17109  #print("Session sample rate: " + str(session.sample_rate))
17110  MakeBoardScreen()
17111  SelectBoard()
17112  bcon.configure(text="Conn", style="GConn.TButton")
17113  devx.set_adc_mux(0)
17114  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x24, 0x0, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set to addr DAC A
17115  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x25, 0x1, 0, 0, 0, 100) # set not addr DAC B
17116 
17120  session.start(0)

17122 def SelectBoard():
17123  global devx, dev0, dev1, dev2, session, BrdSel, CHA, CHB, DevID, RUNstatus, FWRevOne
17124  global PIO_0, PIO_1, PIO_2, PIO_3, PIO_4, PIO_5, PIO_6, PIO_7, cal, SAMPLErate, MaxSamples
17125  global IgnoreFirmwareCheck
17126 
17127  if RUNstatus.get() == 1:
17128  BStop()
17129  print "STOP"
17130 
17131  if BrdSel.get() == 0:
17132  try:
17133  session.remove(dev1)
17134  print "Removing dev1"
17135  except:
17136  print "Skipping dev1"
17137  try:
17138  session.remove(dev2)
17139  print "Removing dev2"
17140  except:
17141  print "Skipping dev2"
17142  session.add(dev0)
17143  devx = dev0
17144  #session.add(devx)
17145  if BrdSel.get() == 1:
17146  try:
17147  session.remove(dev0)
17148  print "Removing dev0"
17149  except:
17150  print "Skipping dev0"
17151  try:
17152  session.remove(dev2)
17153  print "Removing dev2"
17154  except:
17155  print "Skipping dev2"
17156  session.add(dev1)
17157  devx = dev1
17158  #session.add(devx)
17159  DevID = devx.serial
17160  print DevID
17161  print devx.fwver, devx.hwver
17162  print("Session sample rate: " + str(session.sample_rate))
17163  FWRevOne = float(devx.fwver)
17164  if IgnoreFirmwareCheck == 0:
17165  if FWRevOne < 2.17:
17166  showwarning("WARNING","This ALICE version Requires Firmware version > 2.16")
17167  UpdateFirmware()
17168  cal = devx.calibration
17169  CHA = devx.channels['A'] # Open CHA
17170  CHA.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHA in Hi Z split mode
17171  CHB = devx.channels['B'] # Open CHB
17172  CHB.mode = Mode.HI_Z_SPLIT # Put CHB in Hi Z split mode
17173  #
17174  # if session.continuous == 0:
17175  #session.start(0)
17176 
17185  devx.set_adc_mux(0)
17186  if devx.hwver == "F":
17187  print "Rev F Board I/O ports set"
17188  PIO_0 = 28
17189  PIO_1 = 29
17190  PIO_2 = 47
17191  PIO_3 = 3
17192  PIO_4 = 4
17193  PIO_5 = 5
17194  PIO_6 = 6
17195  PIO_7 = 7
17196  else:
17197  PIO_0 = 0
17198  PIO_1 = 1
17199  PIO_2 = 2
17200  PIO_3 = 3
17201  PIO_4 = 4
17202  PIO_5 = 5
17203  PIO_6 = 6
17204  PIO_7 = 7

17270 def onStopfreqScroll(event):
17271  global StopFreqEntry, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, FWRevOne
17272 
17273  onTextScroll(event)
17274  try:
17275  StopFrequency = float(StopFreqEntry.get())
17276  except:
17277  StopFreqEntry.delete(0,"end")
17278  StopFreqEntry.insert(0,50000)
17279  StopFrequency = 50000
17280  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
17281  if StopFrequency >= 50000:
17282  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
17283  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
17284  SetADC_Mux()
17285  else:
17286  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
17287  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
17288  SetADC_Mux()
17289 #
17290 def onStopBodeScroll(event):
17291  global StopBodeEntry, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, FWRevOne
17292 
17293  onTextScroll(event)
17294  try:
17295  StopFrequency = float(StopBodeEntry.get())
17296  except:
17297  StopBodeEntry.delete(0,"end")
17298  StopBodeEntry.insert(0,20000)
17299  StopFrequency = 20000
17300  if FWRevOne > 2.16:
17301  if StopFrequency >= 20000:
17302  Two_X_Sample.set(1)
17303  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
17304  SetADC_Mux()
17305  else:
17306  Two_X_Sample.set(0)
17307  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
17308  SetADC_Mux()

17315 def SetSampleRate():
17316  global SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, AWGSAMPLErate, session, ETSStatus, etssrlab, BaseRateEntry
17317  global Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode
17318 
17319  # ask user for channel to save
17320  BStop() # Force Stop loop if running
17321  try:
17322  NewRate = int(BaseRateEntry.get())
17323  if NewRate <= 100000: # rate has to be less than or equal to 100,000
17324  BaseSampleRate = NewRate
17325  else:
17326  BaseSampleRate = 100000
17327  BaseRateEntry.delete(0,"end")
17328  BaseRateEntry.insert(0,BaseSampleRate)
17329  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate # Scope sample rate
17330  except:
17331  donothing()
17332  session.configure(sample_rate=BaseSampleRate)
17333  # calculate actual sample rate
17334  # minimum clock cycles per sample (100ksps)
17335  m_min_per = 240
17336  # maximum clock cycles per sample (~1024 samples/s)
17337  m_max_per = 24000
17338  sample_time = 1.0 / BaseSampleRate
17339  M1K_timer_clock = 48e6
17340  m_sam_per = round(sample_time * M1K_timer_clock) / 2
17341  if (m_sam_per < m_min_per):
17342  m_sam_per = m_min_per
17343  elif (m_sam_per > m_max_per):
17344  m_sam_per = m_max_per;
17345  # convert back to the actual sample time
17346  sample_time = m_sam_per / M1K_timer_clock
17347  # convert back to the actual sample rate
17348  BaseSampleRate = int(round((1.0 / sample_time) / 2.0))
17349  AWGSAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate
17350  if ETSStatus.get() > 0:
17351  SRstring = "RT Sample Rate = " + str(BaseSampleRate)
17352  etssrlab.config(text=SRstring)
17353  ETSUpdate()
17354  BaseRateEntry.delete(0,"end")
17355  BaseRateEntry.insert(0,BaseSampleRate)
17356  ReMakeAWGwaves() # remake AWG waveforms for new rate
17357 #
17358 def SetADC_Mux():
17359  global devx, SAMPLErate, BaseSampleRate, Two_X_Sample, ADC_Mux_Mode, CHA, CHB
17360  global v1_adc_conf, i1_adc_conf, v2_adc_conf, i2_adc_conf
17361 
17362  if Two_X_Sample.get() == 1:
17363  if ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 0: # VA and VB
17364  devx.set_adc_mux(1)
17365  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 1: # IA and IB
17366  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
17367  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 2: # VA and IB
17368  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
17369  devx.set_adc_mux(2)
17370  # now set new mux values
17371  devx.set_adc_mux(7)
17372  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x20, v1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
17373  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x21, i1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
17374  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, v2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
17375  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, i2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
17376  time.sleep(0.1)
17377  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 3: # VB and IA
17378  # cycle trhough default mux values as starting point
17379  # now set new mux values
17380  devx.set_adc_mux(7)
17381  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x20, v1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
17382  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x21, i1_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U12
17383  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, v2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
17384  devx.ctrl_transfer(0x40, 0x22, i2_adc_conf, 0, 0, 0, 100) # U11
17385  time.sleep(0.1)
17386  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 4: # VA and IA
17387  # now set new mux values
17388  devx.set_adc_mux(4)
17389  elif ADC_Mux_Mode.get() == 5: # VB and IB
17390  # now set new mux values
17391  devx.set_adc_mux(5)
17392  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate * 2 # set to 2X sample mode
17393  else:
17394  devx.set_adc_mux(0)
17395  SAMPLErate = BaseSampleRate

17397 def TraceSelectADC_Mux():
17398  global ADC_Mux_Mode, Alternate_Sweep_Mode, ShowC1_V, ShowC1_I, ShowC2_V, ShowC2_I
17399 
17400  if ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17401  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # All four traces
17402  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
17403  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
17404  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
17405  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
17406  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17407  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
17408  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
17409  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17410  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
17411  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
17412  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17413  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0) # three traces
17414  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(1)
17415  #
17416  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17417  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # IA and IB
17418  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17419  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
17420  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # just IA
17421  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17422  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17423  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(1) # just IB
17424  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17425  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 1 and ShowC1_I.get() == 1 and ShowC2_V.get() == 0 and ShowC2_I.get() == 0:
17426  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(4) # VA and IA
17427  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17428  elif ShowC1_V.get() == 0 and ShowC1_I.get() == 0 and ShowC2_V.get() == 1 and ShowC2_I.get() == 1:
17429  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(5) # VB and IB
17430  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17431  else:
17432  ADC_Mux_Mode.set(0)
17433  Alternate_Sweep_Mode.set(0)
17434  SetADC_Mux()
17435  UpdateTimeTrace()

17437 def UpdateFirmware():
17438  global devx, dev0, dev1, dev2, session, BrdSel, CHA, CHB, DevID, MaxSamples
17439  global bcon, FWRevOne, HWRevOne, FWRevTwo, HWRevTwo, WRevThree, HWRevThree
17440 
17441  RUNstatus.set(0)
17442  if askyesno("Update current firmware","Flash new firmware to current device:\n(Yes) or (No)?"):
17443  filename = askopenfilename(defaultextension = ".bin", filetypes=[("Binary", "*.bin")])
17444  print filename
17445  #print DevID
17446  #print FWRevOne, HWRevOne # devx.fwver, devx.hwver
17447  try:
17448  print "Cancel current session."
17449  session.cancel()
17450  print session.cancelled
17451  session.end()
17452  print "Waiting 5..."
17453  time.sleep(5)
17454  print "Put board in Samba mode and flash firmware."
17455  session.flash_firmware(filename)
17456  except:
17457  showwarning("Complete","Flash Firmware Complete: \n Un-plug board to cycle power.")
17458 
17466  showwarning("Complete","Flash Firmware Complete: \n Un-plug board to cycle power.")
17467  showwarning("Exit ALICE","Must Exit Program: \n Restart ALICE to continue.")
17468  Bcloseexit()

17656 def ETSUpdate():
17657  global FminEntry, MulXEntry, ETSStatus, ETSDisp, ETSDir, ETSts, eqivsamplerate, MaxETSrecord
17658  global SAMPLErate, DivXEntry, FOffEntry, FminDisp, DivX, FOff, MulX, Fmin, FMul, AWGSAMPLErate, TIMEdiv
17659 
17660  if TIMEdiv > 0.2:
17661  MaxETSrecord = int(AWGSAMPLErate * 10 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
17662  else:
17663  MaxETSrecord = int(AWGSAMPLErate * 20 * TIMEdiv / 1000.0)
17664  if (MaxETSrecord*100) > MaxSamples:
17665  MaxETSrecord = MaxSamples / 100
17666  try:
17667  DivX = float(eval(DivXEntry.get()))
17668  if DivX < 2:
17669  DivX = 2
17670  if DivX > 75:
17671  DivX = 75
17672  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
17673  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
17674  except:
17675  DivXEntry.delete(0,END)
17676  DivXEntry.insert(0, DivX)
17677  FOff = 25
17678  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
17679  while MulX > MaxETSrecord:
17680  FOff = FOff + 5
17681  MulX = (DivX*SAMPLErate)/(100*FOff)
17682  FOff = 0 - FOff
17683  SRstring = "Rec Len Mul = " + str(MulX) + " samples"
17684  MulXEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
17685  SRstring = "Offset = " + str(FOff) + " samples"
17686  FOffEntry.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
17687  baseFreq = SAMPLErate/DivX
17688  try:
17689  FMul = float(eval(FminEntry.get()))
17690  if FMul < 1:
17691  FMul = 1
17692  FminEntry.delete(0,END)
17693  FminEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
17694  if FMul > 75:
17695  FMul = 75
17696  FminEntry.delete(0,END)
17697  FminEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
17698  except:
17699  FminEntry.delete(0,END)
17700  FminEntry.insert(0, int(FMul))
17701  Fmin = baseFreq * FMul
17702  SRstring = "Multiplied Freq = " + ' {0:.1f} '.format(Fmin) + " Hz"
17703  FminDisp.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value
17704  SRstring = "Base Frequency = " + ' {0:.2f} '.format(baseFreq) + " Hz"
17705  eqivsamplerate.config(text = SRstring) # change displayed value

17875 def SettingsUpdate():
17876  global GridWidth, TRACEwidth, TRACEaverage, Vdiv, HarmonicMarkers, ZEROstuffing, RevDate
17877  global Settingswindow, SettingsStatus, SettingsDisp, ZSTuff, TAvg, VDivE, TwdthE, GwdthE, HarMon
17878  global CHA_TC1, CHA_TC2, CHB_TC1, CHB_TC2
17879  global CHA_A1, CHA_A2, CHB_A1, CHB_A2
17880  global cha_TC1Entry, cha_TC2Entry, chb_TC1Entry, chb_TC2Entry
17881  global cha_A1Entry, cha_A2Entry, chb_A1Entry, chb_A2Entry
17882 
17883  try:
17884  GW = int(eval(GwdthE.get()))
17885  if GW < 1:
17886  GW = 1
17887  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
17888  GwdthE.insert(0, int(GW))
17889  if GW > 5:
17890  GW = 5
17891  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
17892  GwdthE.insert(0, int(GW))
17893  except:
17894  GwdthE.delete(0,END)
17895  GwdthE.insert(0, GridWidth.get())
17896  GridWidth.set(GW)
17897  try:
17898  TW = int(eval(TwdthE.get()))
17899  if TW < 1:
17900  TW = 1
17901  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
17902  TwdthE.insert(0, int(TW))
17903  if TW > 5:
17904  TW = 5
17905  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
17906  TwdthE.insert(0, int(TW))
17907  except:
17908  TwdthE.delete(0,END)
17909  TwdthE.insert(0, TRACEwidth.get())
17910  TRACEwidth.set(TW)
17911  # Number of average sweeps for average mode
17912  try:
17913  TA = int(eval(TAvg.get()))
17914  if TA < 1:
17915  TA = 1
17916  TAvg.delete(0,END)
17917  TAvg.insert(0, int(TA))
17918  if TA > 16:
17919  TA = 16
17920  TAvg.delete(0,END)
17921  TAvg.insert(0, int(TA))
17922  except:
17923  TAvg.delete(0,END)
17924  TAvg.insert(0, TRACEaverage.get())
17925  TRACEaverage.set(TA)
17926  # Number of vertical divisions for spectrum / Bode
17927  try:
17928  VDv = int(eval(VDivE.get()))
17929  if VDv < 1:
17930  VDv = 1
17931  VDivE.delete(0,END)
17932  VDivE.insert(0, int(VDv))
17933  if VDv > 16:
17934  VDv = 16
17935  VDivE.delete(0,END)
17936  VDivE.insert(0, int(VDv))
17937  except:
17938  VDivE.delete(0,END)
17939  VDivE.insert(0, Vdiv.get())
17940  Vdiv.set(VDv)
17941  # number of Harmonic Markers in SA
17942  try:
17943  HM = int(eval(HarMon.get()))
17944  if HM < 1:
17945  HM = 1
17946  HarMon.delete(0,END)
17947  HarMon.insert(0, int(HM))
17948  if HM > 9:
17949  HM =9
17950  HarMon.delete(0,END)
17951  HarMon.insert(0, int(HM))
17952  except:
17953  HarMon.delete(0,END)
17954  HarMon.insert(0, HarmonicMarkers.get())
17955  HarmonicMarkers.set(HM)
17956  # The zero stuffing value is 2 ** ZERO stuffing, calculated on initialize
17957  try:
17958  ZST = int(eval(ZSTuff.get()))
17959  if ZST < 1:
17960  ZST = 1
17961  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
17962  ZSTuff.insert(0, int(ZST))
17963  if ZST > 5:
17964  ZST = 5
17965  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
17966  ZSTuff.insert(0, int(ZST))
17967  except:
17968  ZSTuff.delete(0,END)
17969  ZSTuff.insert(0, ZEROstuffing.get())
17970  ZEROstuffing.set(ZST)
17971 #
17972  try:
17973  TC1A = float(cha_TC1Entry.get())
17974  CHA_TC1.set(TC1A)
17975  if TC1A < 0:
17976  TC1A = 0
17977  cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
17978  cha_TC1Entry.insert(0, TC1A)
17979  except:
17980  cha_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
17981  cha_TC1Entry.insert(0, CHA_TC1.get())
17982  try:
17983  TC2A = float(cha_TC2Entry.get())
17984  CHA_TC2.set(TC2A)
17985  if TC2A < 0:
17986  TC2A = 0
17987  cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
17988  cha_TC2Entry.insert(0, TC2A)
17989  except:
17990  cha_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
17991  cha_TC2Entry.insert(0, CHA_TC2.get())
17992  #
17993  try:
17994  Gain1A = float(cha_A1Entry.get())
17995  CHA_A1.set(Gain1A)
17996  except:
17997  cha_A1Entry.delete(0,END)
17998  cha_A1Entry.insert(0, CHA_A1.get())
17999  try:
18000  Gain2A = float(cha_A2Entry.get())
18001  CHA_A2.set(Gain2A)
18002  except:
18003  cha_A2Entry.delete(0,END)
18004  cha_A2Entry.insert(0, CHA_A2.get())
18005  #
18006  try:
18007  TC1B = float(chb_TC1Entry.get())
18008  CHB_TC1.set(TC1B)
18009  if TC1B < 0:
18010  TC1B = 0
18011  chb_TC1Entry.delete(0, END)
18012  chb_TC1Entry.insert(0, TC1B)
18013  except:
18014  chb_TC1Entry.delete(0,END)
18015  chb_TC1Entry.insert(0, CHB_TC1.get())
18016  try:
18017  TC2B = float(chb_TC2Entry.get())
18018  CHB_TC2.set(TC2B)
18019  if TC2B < 0:
18020  TC2B = 0
18021  chb_TC2Entry.delete(0, END)
18022  chb_TC2Entry.insert(0, TC2B)
18023  except:
18024  chb_TC2Entry.delete(0,END)
18025  chb_TC2Entry.insert(0, CHB_TC2.get())
18026  #
18027  try:
18028  Gain1B = float(chb_A1Entry.get())
18029  CHB_A1.set(Gain1B)
18030  except:
18031  chb_A1Entry.delete(0,END)
18032  chb_A1Entry.insert(0, CHB_A1.get())
18033  try:
18034  Gain2B = float(chb_A2Entry.get())
18035  CHB_A2.set(Gain2B)
18036  except:
18037  chb_A2Entry.delete(0,END)
18038  chb_A2Entry.insert(0, CHB_A2.get())
18039  #
18040 def DestroySettings():

18043  SettingsStatus.set(0)
18044  SettingsUpdate()

18055 TgInput = IntVar(0) # Trigger Input variable
